1,"meta":{"title":"","description":""},"masterProductID":52171,"name":"Fresh Step Multi-Cat Clumping Litter With Febreze Freshness, Bag","primary_category_id":"200152","primary_category_name":"Litter","short_description":"FS MULTICAT W/FEBREZE BAG 42 LB       90","images":{"large":"https://s7d2.scene7.com/is/image/PetSmart/5288001?$sclp-prd-main_large$","small":"https://s7d2.scene7.com/is/image/PetSmart/5288001?$sclp-prd-main_small$"},"personalization":{"styleOptions":{},"textLocations":{}},"merchandisingHierarchy":{"category":"C FS Cly Clmp L","class":"C Fresh Step L","department":"C Litter","division":"C Cons","vicePresidentId":3,"vicePresidentName":"Consumables"},"inventory":["ps_us_web_inv",1113,3132,52,2522,3073,1190,109,110,1522,1291,1838,1220,1218,1148,2372,373,2378,2161,1449,2527,1402,2160,449,1706,2278,395,208,1228,173,131,2630,1487,1554,3294,3299,3283,2267,63,1959,3290,3211,379,1266,1164,1078,2449,737,146,2217,2093,2162,2501,1348,3052,3307,1056,2271,2130,619,1142,2399,1239,1039,2312,1700,3250,1314,1896,2537,1004,1282,1245,2386,2296,631,1526,2186,2334,2421,2436,2237,1708,2218,2529,1614,2706,1003,787,2493,2558,727,75,1042,3284,1293,2465,2280,1034,1193,82,1095,1551,1427,1163,1250,3047,3309,1854,2442,292,1255,1461,1961,1565,2506,2273,97,1310,625,1281,196,1736,1796,2109,2715,3011,2359,1455,2223,76,1393,781,3226,166,2486,2084,1541,457,383,1144,2208,1251,2165,3062,1812,50,1701,59,2719,1248,416,324,2616,1932,61,381,2631,1265,83,54,72,1419,3101,1192,2354,2279,2780,2462,2443,2373,3180,1230,1143,1498,1536,1188,56,1229,2521,389,1398,1114,1031,386,1072,2304,2260,2188,150,2051,2539,2258,49,269,1070,2466,1121,1125,145,1100,3046,2231,1092,1075,2475,2288,74,2789,2611,762,1232,1184,348,673,1117,1413,2294,1599,471,1074,2349,1344,1963,2180,1519,2720,1167,2502,399,310,1733,186,2187,635,3105,1361,1294,1236,417,454,219,2483,105,99,98],"size":{"solidSize":"42 Lb"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":8.5,"cartonLength":9.5,"cartonWeight":42.5,"cartonWidth":14},"package":null,"brand":"Fresh Step","customCategory":"Litter","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eFight litter box odors in your multi-cat home with Fresh Step Multi-Cat Clumping Litter. Featuring an extra-strength formula, this Fresh Step clumping cat litter delivers even more odor-fighting protection with the power of Febreze to leave behind a fresh, clean scent. Made with natural clay plus built in odor defense, this clumping clay litter uses activated charcoal and Ammonia Block technology to guarantee 15 days of odor control in your multi-cat litter box (1). Featuring ClumpLock technology, the Fresh Step litter locks in liquid and cat urine odor on contact to form tight clumps. This makes scooping your kitty litter box quick and effortless, and it helps prevent crumbles from being left behind. In addition to easy cat litter clumping, the scented cat litter has a low-dust formula to help keep surfaces cleaner in your home. Enjoy more catnaps and cuddle time with your kitty when you choose Fresh Step cat litter.(1) See package for more information on termsand conditions\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFRESH STEP CLUMPING CAT LITTER: Four 10.5-lb. pouches of Fresh Step Multi-Cat Clumping Litter with Febreze freshness, an extra-strength formula designed for multi-cat homes\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003e15 DAYS OF ODOR CONTROL: Ammonia Block technology and activated charcoal help eliminate the strongest multi cat litter box odors and guarantee 15 days of odor control (1)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eRAPID LIQUID ABSORPTION: Fresh Step Clumping Cat Litter quickly absorbs liquid, ensuring a dry and clean litter box environment for your cat's comfort\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFORMS TIGHT CLUMPS: Fresh Step ClumpLock technology locks in liquid and odor on contact and causes immediate kitty litter clumping to make scooping easy and prevent crumbles from being left behind\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFRESH, CLEAN SMELL: Fresh Step litter multi cat formula combines natural clay with carbon, Ammonia Block Technology and Febreze freshness for next-level odor control\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eLOW-DUST FORMULA: Low-dust cat litter multi-cat formula helps keep your floors and other surfaces cleaner\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFIND YOUR FRESH STEP: Whether you have one fab feline or a family of fur friends, explore Fresh Step\u0026#39;s full line of cat litter formulas to find the purr-fect litter for you. \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFor best results, do not mix with non clumping cat litter. For first time use, start with an empty, clean cat litter box. Fill it with 3 to 4 inches of Fresh Step Cat Litter. Remove clumps and solids daily and dispose in trash. Do not flush. The rest of the litter stays fresh. Add more Fresh Step Cat Litter to refresh your litter box each time you scoop. Maintain level of litter at 3 to 4 inches.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCats\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFresh Step\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eAs a reminder, especially to pregnant women and immunosuppressed persons, cat feces can sometimes transmit a disease called toxoplasmosis. Therefore, always remember to wash hands thoroughly after handling used cat litter. For further information, consult your doctor. Unused cat litter poses no toxoplasmosis threat. Caution: Do not use this product as a traction aid because product becomes slippery and slick when wet.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e42 lb\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1555891200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"litter-features":["Advanced Odor Control","Clumping","Low Dust","Multi-Cat","Scented"],"litter-materials":["Clay"],"litter-types":["Clay"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["Fresh Step Multi Pack"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.7,"bvReviewCount":35373,"conversionRate":90,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"CLOROX (FDC)","manufacturerSku":"10044600320493","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":false,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"44600320496","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":19.19,"strikethrough-number":27.99,"validUntil":"2035-01-01T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$19.19-$25.99","strikethrough":"$25.99-$27.99"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["2 Sizes"],"categories":[[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"60080122","name":{"default":"Timezone Test"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"5000034","name":{"default":"Fresh Step"}},{"id":"5000000","name":{"default":"Featured Brands"}}],[{"id":"PERKSPOT","name":{"default":"15 OFF 75"}},{"id":"Product-Assortments","name":{"default":"PA"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"SDDBOPIS","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery In Store Pick Up"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"60000060","name":{"default":"Curbside and In Store Pickup"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"200152","name":{"default":"Litter"}},{"id":"200211","name":{"default":"Litter and Waste Disposal"}},{"id":"200000","name":{"default":"Cat"}}],[{"id":"0824-SameDayDelivery-Sale","name":{"default":"Save on Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"Product-Assortments","name":{"default":"PA"}}],[{"id":"0824-Same-Day-Delivery-Sale","name":{"def