":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e Dr. Elsey\u0026#39;s is a veterinarian-owned cat product brand dedicated to creating products that solve the complex needs of pet owners. Founded in 1987 with the first all-natural clumping cat litter, Dr. Elsey\u0026#39;s line of products has since grown to include a variety of premium litters that address the health and behavioral needs of cats in every stage of life. With the mission to enhance the lives of pets to the degree in which they enrich ours, Dr. Elsey\u0026#39;s strives to put heart, soul and science into their line of specialty cat litters and food. Our #1 selling litter - Dr. Elsey\u0026#39;s Ultra Clumping Cat Litter has superior odor control and is perfect for multi-cat families and those cat owners with sifting or mechanical litter boxes. 100% Money Back Guarantee!\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eOur #1 selling litter - Dr. Elsey\u0026#39;s Ultra Clumping Cat Litter has superior odor control and is perfect for multi-cat families and those cat owners with sifting or mechanical litter boxes. \u003cli\u003eUltra\u0026#39;s unique formulation combines heavier non-tracking granules with medium grain clay.\u003cli\u003e The result is an excellent clumping litter that prevents moisture from reaching the bottom of the litter box, while providing a clump that will not break apart.\u003cli\u003e Ultra controls odor naturally without perfumes or deodorants.\u003cli\u003e Backed by our 100% satisfaction guarantee! \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eEnvironment Type:\u003c/b\u003e Indoors\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eSpecies:\u003c/b\u003e Cat\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eScented/Unscented:\u003c/b\u003e Unscented\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eClumping/Non-Clumping:\u003c/b\u003e Clumping\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eMaterials:\u003c/b\u003e Natural Clay\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eProduct Dimensions:\u003c/b\u003e 26 in x 15 in x 4 in\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003ePackage Weight:\u003c/b\u003e 40 lb Bag\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eInstructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFill clean, dry litter box with 3 to 4 inches of Dr. Elsey\u0026#39;s litter. 2) Scoop waste twice daily and refill as necessary. 3) Dispose of used litter in trash. Do not flush!\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCautions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Always wash your hands thoroughly after handling the litter box. A parasite sometimes found in cat feces can cause toxoplasmosis. Encouraging your cat to use an indoor litter box, or properly disposing of outdoor cat feces, is beneficial to overall water quality. Please do not flush cat litter in toilets or dispose of it outdoors in gutters or storm drains.","onlineFrom":1388534400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"litter-features":["Clumping","Low Dust","Low Tracking","Multi-Cat","Unscented"],"litter-materials":["Clay"],"litter-types":["Clay"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.3,"bvReviewCount":2716,"conversionRate":75,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"PRECIOUS CAT (FDC)","manufacturerSku":"404404","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"338004404","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":22.99,"strikethrough-number":null,"validUntil":"","formatted":{"primary":"$12.99-$22.99","strikethrough":"$15.99-$22.99"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["2 Sizes"],"categories":[[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name"