2,392,2513,435,503,1640,157,446,233,53,1307,2495,3117,81,390,1303,52,75,2449,1708,3049,1422,378,2283,3040,1230,290,283,624,648,186,3108,509,3234,2512,1458,1562,361,2787,2442,449,1572,779,2481,2576,638,1921,2212,1028,3012,1004,1166,217,192,196,188,1736,1732,214,2064,1352,1596,619,744,2376,1044,649,215,620,179,1120,1966,1074,1252,3080,1245,431,268,2383,412,1057,1278,2308,1819,2484,83,3068,2708,2471,1006,1296,622,1953,2521,178,1221,3021,3151,3016,789,2753,3005,1031,1122,2349,1244,3180,3047,529,3301,2479,2235,2525,3273,1036,2111,519,2619,1183,2555,2622,1071,385,2462,725,3046,310,2717],"size":{"solidSize":"30 Lb"},"flavor":{"value":"Salmon \u0026 Rice","displays":"Fish, Salmon"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":5,"cartonLength":24,"cartonWeight":30.3,"cartonWidth":20},"package":null,"brand":"Purina Pro Plan","customCategory":"Dry Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eNurture your dog's sensitive skin and stomach with Purina Pro Plan Brand Dog Food Sensitive Skin and Stomach Salmon and Rice Formula adult dry dog food. Nutrient\u0026ndash;rich salmon is the first ingredient and a high\u0026ndash;quality source of protein in this formula. Also containing prebiotic fiber, this dog food for sensitive stomachs boasts a highly digestible formula and nourishes the beneficial bacteria found in your dog's intestine for his digestive health. Ingredients such as rice and oatmeal provide easily digestible sources of carbohydrates for your dog. Meanwhile, fish oil \r\n- rich in EPA, one of the omega-3 fatty acids - helps support healthy joints and mobility, while omega-6 fatty acids and vitamin A nourish your dog's skin and keep his coat looking healthy. There is also no corn, wheat or soy in our Sensitive Skin and Stomach Formula. It's important to know the food you choose for your dog will help keep him healthy, happy and feeling extraordinary, andthat's what Purina Pro Plan Brand Dog Food Sensitive Skin and Stomach Salmon and Rice Formula adult dry dog food does.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eOat meal is easily digestible and gentle on the digestive system. High protein formula, with real salmon as the first ingredient. Complete and balanced adult dog food formula fortified with guaranteed live probiotics for digestive and immune health. Used to be known as FOCUS Sensitive Skin and Stomach Salmon and Rice Formula. Sunflower oil rich in omega\u0026ndash;6 fatty acids for healthy skin and coat. Natural prebiotic fiber nourishes specific intestinal bacteria for digestive health. Antioxidants for a healthy immune system. Fish oil rich in omega\u0026ndash;3 fatty acids for joint health and mobility. Salmon offers a nutrient\u0026ndash;rich high\u0026ndash;quality source of protein. Made without artificial colors or flavors. Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePro Plan Sensitive Skin \u0026#38; Stomach Formula\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eKibble, Crunchy\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCorn Free, No Animal By\u0026ndash;Products, No Artificial Colors, No Artificial Flavors, Poultry Free, Soy Free, Wheat Free, High\u0026ndash;Protein, Real Meat, With Vitamins, Prebiotic\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eAllergy, Bone Health, Digestive Health, Sensitive Skin, Sensitive Stomach, Skin \u0026#38; Coat, Veterinarian Recommended, Gastrointestinal, Heart Health, Immune Support\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eSalmon\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e30.4 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eSalmon, Rice, Barley, Canola Meal, Oat Meal, Fish Meal, Salmon Meal, Beef Fat Preserved With Mixed\u0026ndash;Tocopherols, Dried Yeast, Natural Flavor, Sunflower Oil, Fish Oil, Dried Chicory Root, Calcium Carbonate, Salt, Potassium Chloride, L\u0026ndash;Lysine Monohydrochloride, VITAMINS [Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Vitamin A Supplement, Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement], Taurine, MINERALS [Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite], Dl\u0026ndash;Methionine, Choline Chloride, L\u0026ndash;Ascorbyl\u0026ndash;2\u0026ndash;Polyphosphate (Vitamin C). M444922\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (Min)...26.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...16.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...4.0%, Moisture (Max)...12.0%, Linoleic Acid (Min)...1.5%, Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) (Min)...0.1%, Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA), (Min)...0.1%, Calcium (Ca) (Min)...1.0%, Phosphorus (P) (Min)...0.8%, Selenium (Se) (Min)...0.35 mg/kg, Vitamin A (Min)...15,000 IU/kg, Vitamin E (Min)...460 IU/kg, Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C)* (Min)...70 mg/kg, Glucosamine* (Min)...350 ppm, Omega\u0026ndash;3 Fatty Acids* (Min)...0.75%, Omega\u0026ndash;6 Fatty Acids* (Min)...1.6% *Not recognized as an essential nutrient by the AAFCO Dog Food Nutrient Profiles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e3,903 kcal/kg, 449 kcal/cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eAlthough you\u0026#39;ll be anxious to see the difference Pro Plan can make in your dog, please allow 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days to ease the transition from your dog\u0026#39;s current food. Each day, simply feed a little less of the previous food and a little more Pro Plan until you\u0026#39;re feeding Pro Plan exclusively. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eDog\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Specialized Nutrition","onlineFrom":1464998400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodForms":["Bags"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["Sensitive Skin","Sensitive Stomach"],"kibbleSizes":["Medium Breed"],"nutritionalOptions":["With-Grain"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["Pro Plan Digestion \u0026 Skin Health","Pro Plan Specialized"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.4,"bvReviewCount":8014,"conversionRate":30,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA DRY","manufacturerSku":"00-38100-17552","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"38100175526","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":77.48,"strikethrough-number":null,"validUntil":"","formatted":{"primary":"$20.68-$94.98","strikethrough":"$20.68-$97.98"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["4 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"S03-Dog","name":{"default":"Dog Sale"}},{"id":"S03","name":{"default":"March"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"TEST---Spend-75-get-15-off","name":{"default":"Spend $75+ get $15 off"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"5000085","name":{"default":"Dog"}},{"id":"5000083","name":{"default":"Purina Pro Plan"}},{"id":"5000000","name":{"default":"Featured Brands"}}],[{"id":"S03Dog-10X","name":{"def