2304,2459,2423,2271,1826,3294,73,1121,1107,1682,98,1802,1242,447,2327,2329,2511,1817,1565,1004,3105,2572,2301,2228,2229,3050,1648,1987,1042,3073,2542,1366,454,1308,1268,1946,208,110,192,373,2527,2133,378,624,3179,1775,413,390,1133,2233,2558,1519,3284,1011,1239,1245,1071,2237,1900,306,1452,1376,2528,1364,1114,570,1235,2480,3087,2226,1188,2038,580,3020,3253,582,2308,3047,1372,356,3103,1568,602,2560,1392,2539,411,2622,352,3069,2065,3008,409,3175,1878,609,3048,1856,1335,2424,3080,2372,2334,1862,1759,1921,1102,132,3147,1343,2113,2730,1894,2502,1293,1884,349,1550,2419,431,2507,1579,1352,1599,1401,1101,178,472,1421,324,1747,1807,2180,1838,209,1577,1406,2784,1058,1110,1100,334,128,2724,2776,2143,2710,1294,2125,469,1193,3072,2735,1218,1162,1045,459,1503,1007,1231,739,2299,727,637,1729,596,2501,2443,204,1689,2436,744,308,1005,3283,1079,3011,1662,1354,1103,1714,638,3151,203,1486,3132,575,788,2749,305,3123,1752,1064,1506,2434,598,443,1457,1934,2529,1581,1072,1857,237,1589,1961,1706,1651,3278,2500,3027,2442,1197,594,2208,343,2199,1962,1322,2093,361,1571,1353,1233,1522,231,1184,2447,50,1601,81,1975,1340,52,2616,131,1332,2611,2277,3067,3028,2581,1361,55,1183,790,1056,1959,1806,2278,1700,1719,318,72,670,1413,1328,76,1419,49,2300,1953,3235,1551,242,56,2218,2755,97,1270,2751,2486,252,2330,1835,1701,332,792,2316,2215,1365,2404,600,3279,357,2481,2466,3300,1593,1348,1146,3118,230,2361,3259,729,2191,2207,2161,414,1869,2160,243,2717,1580,2130,2576,280,294,269,2188,233,320,649,2469,1398,354,1244,1309,1497,2721,2212,502,1057,1096,2204,1788,2522,1574,1850,2247,2631,401,673,1481,1449,2373,1281,2109,2128,3055,146,1427,1731,416,2619,1386,2238,3046,2705,1760,2398,103,3098,2317,63,1488,3236,1393,1207,142,374,171,1933,781,1650,572,2294,1707,1566,2567,1070,347,3035,3301,1031,1163,632,2415,2707,1148,3258,785,1431,1226,1742,605,1970,1084,405,2747,273,1173,1251,1265,129,3273,1385,2217,441,2273,221,1234,737,169,2267,2435,1269,516,2044,675,1423,1167,1217,1455,1705,3250,1108,248,1014,246,386,668,2390,1015,629,1279,2460,2538,1051,61,1521,398,288,358,3282,313,1828,1010,247,1830,1243,463,284,1081,2421,375,2069,1966,148],"size":{"solidSize":"42 Lb"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":8.5,"cartonLength":9.5,"cartonWeight":42.5,"cartonWidth":14},"package":null,"brand":"Fresh Step","customCategory":"Litter","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eGet total odor control in your cat's litter box with Fresh Step Simply Unscented Clumping Litter. Formulated with natural clay plus built-in odor defense, activated charcoal and Ammonia Block Technology, this unscented cat litter fights 100% of litter odors (1) without the use of added fragrances or dyes. Fresh Step cat litter unscented formula guarantees 15 days of odor control in your cat's litter box (2). Fresh Step ClumpLock Technology locks in liquid and cat urine odor on contact to form tight clumps and make scooping easy. In addition to easy cat litter clumping, this fragrance-free litter has a low-dust formula to help keep your floors and cat litter box area cleaner. Enjoy more catnaps and cuddle time with your kitty when you choose Fresh Step cat litter.(1) Ammonia and fecal malodor(2) See package for more information on terms and conditions\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eCLUMPING CAT LITTER: Four 10.5-lb. pouches of Fresh Step Simply Unscented Clumping Litter, activated charcoal kitty litter that keeps litter boxes smelling fresh\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003e15 DAYS OF ODOR CONTROL: Fresh Step unscented cat litter combines natural clay with carbon and Ammonia Block Technology for 15 days of kitty litter box odor control (2)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eRAPID LIQUID ABSORPTION: Fresh Step Clumping Cat Litter quickly absorbs liquid, ensuring a dry and clean litter box environment for your cat's comfort\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFORMS TIGHT CLUMPS: Fresh Step ClumpLock technology locks in liquid and odor on contact and causes immediate kitty litter clumping to make scooping easy and prevent crumbles from being left behind\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eNO ADDED DYES OR FRAGRANCES: Unscented litter uses clay, carbon and minerals to help stop cat urine and waste odors without the use of added fragrances or dyes\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eLOW-DUST FORMULA: Low-dust Fresh Step cat clumping litter formula helps keep your floors and cat litter box area cleaner\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFIND YOUR FRESHSTEP: Whether you have one fab feline or a family of fur friends, explore Fresh Step\u0026#39;s full line of cat litter formulas to find the purr-fect litter for you. \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eFor best results, do not mix with non-clumping cat litter. For first time use, start with an empty, clean cat litter box. Fill your clean litter box with 3 to 4 inches of Fresh Step Simply Unscented Cat Litter. Remove clumps and solids daily and dispose in trash. Do not flush. The rest of the litter stays fresh. Add more litter to refresh your litter box each time you scoop. Maintain level of litter at 3 to 4 inches.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCats\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFresh Step\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eAs a reminder, especially to pregnant women and immunosuppressed persons, cat feces can sometimes transmit a disease called toxoplasmosis. Therefore, always remember to wash hands thoroughly after handling used cat litter. For further information, consult your doctor. Unused cat litter poses no toxoplasmosis threat. Caution: Do not use this product as a traction aid because product becomes slippery and slick when wet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e42 lb\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1555891200000,"onlineTo