h":9.5,"cartonWeight":36.1,"cartonWidth":12},"package":{"height":16,"length":12,"weight":35,"width":9.5},"brand":"Tidy Cats","customCategory":"Litter","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eTidy Cats cat litter believes home should smell like home. That's why they've created Tidy Cats Free and Clean Unscented Cat Litter. This low dust cat litter provides the odor control you have come to expect from Tidy Cats cat litter, but free from fragrances and dyes. This natural clay multicat clumping litter with activated charcoal absorbs odors to provide powerful clumping cat litter odor control. Activated charcoal utilizes microscopic pores to trap odor for a litter freshener that's effective and long\u0026ndash;lasting. Experience an unscented odor control cat litter that boasts strong cat litter clumping for easy scooping and cleaning. This low dust cat litter also provides a mess free, peace of mind pouring. Whether you're a single cat home or use cat litter boxes for multiple cats, Tidy Cats Free and Clean is a scoopable cat litter that's unscented and undeniably effective.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures: \u003c/b\u003eUnscented cat litter provides long\u0026ndash;lasting litter box odor control without fragrances or dyes, Activated charcoal and clay provides effective clumping cat litter odor control, Strong, tight forming clumps makes cat litter box easy cleaning, Low dust cat litter for less mess, peace of mind pouring, Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures: \u003c/b\u003eOdor Control\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e5276505\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePurina Tidy Cats Free and Clean Unscented Cat Litter\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eMaterials: \u003c/b\u003ePlastic\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u