,1733,128,2722,2466,1390,83,514,1042,1529,444,638,1277,2296,1902,2778,1475,1102,1238,557,2131,2330,2421,1092,774,3017,1239,1661,2125,2473,2407,1108,2314,1381,1316,2169],"size":{"solidSize":"38 Lb"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":13.69,"cartonLength":7,"cartonWeight":39.51,"cartonWidth":11.75},"package":{"height":13.69,"length":7,"weight":39.51,"width":11.75},"brand":"Arm \u0026 Hammer","customCategory":"Litter","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e It\u0026#39;s time to end scraping and scrubbing with Arm \u0026 Hammer SLIDE Easy Clean-Up Clumping Litter. Our revolutionary formula means the litter slides right out of the litter box, making cleanup easy. Plus, Clump \u0026 Seal technology seals and destroys odor for a 7-Day Odor-Free Home, Guaranteed. Fellow cat lovers like you put their trust in ARM \u0026 HAMMER. Join them and see how quick and easy clean-up can be!\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003e Superior Odor Control for a 7 Day Odor Free Home - Guaranteed \u003cli\u003e Revolutionary non-stick litter slides right out for easy cleaning. No scraping. No scrubbing. No problem \u003cli\u003e Moisture-activated micro-granules form a tight seal around cat waste, while plant derived particles help create rock-hard clumps for easy scooping \u003cli\u003e 99.9% Dust Free. No more dust clouds when pouring or scooping \u003cli\u003e Strong enough for Multi-Cat households and also available in Non-Stop Odor Control, a freshly scented continuous action formula \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eMaterial:\u003c/b\u003e Limestone, Bentonite, Baking Soda with proprietary blends\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eEnvironment Type:\u003c/b\u003e Indoors\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eSpecies:\u003c/b\u003e Cats\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor:\u003c/b\u003e Gray\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003ePackage Weight:\u003c/b\u003e 38 lb\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCleaning Instructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 1) Start with a clean, empty litter box.\u003cbr\u003e  2) Fill 3-4 inches of SLIDE litter.\u003cbr\u003e  3) Scoop regularly and add litter to maintain 3-4 inches. \u003cbr\u003e 4) When it\u0026#39;s time to change the litter, SLIDE pours right out.\u003cbr\u003e  5) You may never have to scrape or scrub again!\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaution:\u003c/b\u003e Litter seals in and destroys odors, forming rock-solid clumps. Remove clumps and solid waste daily to keep the rest of the litter fresh. Add more Arm \u0026 Hammer SLIDE to replace what you have scooped out and maintain a depth of 3-4 inches. Dispose of used litter in trash. Do not flush or put in drains.\u003cbr\u003e","onlineFrom":1519257600000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"litter-features":["Advanced Odor Control","Clumping","Low Dust","Low Tracking","Scented"],"litter-materials":["Clay"],"litter-types":["Clay"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store","Online"],"series":["Arm \u0026 Hammer Premium Litter"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.2,"bvReviewCount":6194,"conversionRate":70,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"CHURCH AND DWIGHT CO INC","manufacturerSku":"20505070","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"33200974284","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":26.79,"strikethrough-number":28.99,"validUntil":"2028-01-01T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$14.89-$26.79","strikethrough":"$17.99-$28.99"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["3 Sizes"],"categories":[[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"60080122","name":