this high protein dog food delivers the outstanding nutrition he needs for everyday excellence and the great taste he deserves. This chicken dog food with rice doesn't compromise on nutrition or flavor, while a high protein level helps support strong muscles, including a healthy heart. Vitamin A and linoleic acid, an omega\u0026ndash;6 fatty acid, help promote healthy skin and a shiny coat. This adult dog food also supports your dog's digestive and immune health with guaranteed live probiotics for dogs to help maintain gut microbiome resilience. Natural prebiotic fiber nourishes the beneficial bacteria in his digestive tract. Watch your dog enjoy the dual\u0026ndash;textured experience of crunchy dog kibble and tender shredded pieces, providing a unique contrast dogs love.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCrunchy dog kibble combined with tender, shredded pieces for taste and texture dogs love. High protein dog food dry recipe, with real chicken as the first ingredient, Real meat dog food fortified with live probiotics for dogs to help maintain gut microbiome resilience, Vitamin A and omega\u0026ndash;6 fatty acids to nourish skin and coat. Natural prebiotic fiber for dogs helps deliver digestive support, Dry dog food with a high protein level to support strong muscles, including a healthy heart. Contains rice, an excellent source of carbohydrates for energy, Ingredients are carefully selected to provide key nutrients pets need. Purina Pro Plan dog food offering 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for adult dogs, Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePro Plan Complete Essentials\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eKibble, Crunchy, Hard, Semi\u0026ndash;Moist, Shredded\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAllBreeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCarrageenan Free, No Artificial Colors, No Artificial Flavors, Potato Free, High\u0026ndash;Protein, Real Meat, With Vitamins, High Fiber, Omegas, Prebiotic, Probiotics\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eBone Health, Dental, Digestive Health, Growth Support, Appetite Support, Energy \u0026#38; Vitality Support, Eye Health, Gastrointestinal, Hip \u0026#38; Joint Support, Immune Support, Muscle Support\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eChicken\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e35.4 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eChicken, Rice, Whole Grain Wheat, Poultry By\u0026ndash;Product Meal, Whole Grain Corn, Soybean Meal, Beef Fat Preserved With Mixed\u0026ndash;Tocopherols, Corn Protein Meal, Dried Egg Product, Natural Flavor, Dried Beet Pulp, Glycerin, Mono And Dicalcium Phosphate, Wheat Bran, Calcium Carbonate, Fish Meal, Salt, Soybean Oil, Potassium Chloride, MINERALS [Zinc Proteinate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Proteinate, Copper Proteinate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite], VITAMINS [Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement], Choline Chloride, Dried Bacillus Coagulans Fermentation Product, L\u0026ndash;Ascorbyl\u0026ndash;2\u0026ndash;Polyphosphate (Vitamin C), L\u0026ndash;Lysine Monohydrochloride, Garlic Oil. A445523\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (Min)...26.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...16.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...3.0%, Moisture (Max)...12.0%, Linoleic Acid (Min)...1.4%, Calcium (Ca) (Min)...1.0%, Phosphorus (P) (Min)...0.8%, Selenium (Se) (Min)...0.35 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin A (Min)...15,000 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin E (Min)...460 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C)* (Min)...70 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Glucosamine* (Min)...400 ppm, Omega\u0026ndash;6 Fatty Acids* (Min)...1.5%, Bacillus coagulans* (Min)...600 million CFU\u0026frasl;lb *Not recognized as an essential nutrient by the AAFCO Dog Food Nutrient Profiles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e3790 kcal/kg, 369 kcal/cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eMAKING THE SWITCH TO PRO PLAN: Although you'll be anxious to see the difference Pro Plan can make in your dog, please allow 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days to ease the transition from your dog's current food. Each day, simply feed a little less of the previous food and a little more Pro Plan until you're feeding Pro Plan exclusively. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eDog\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Specialized Nutrition","onlineFrom":1370995200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodForms":["Bags"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"kibbleSizes":["Medium Breed"],"nutritionalOptions":["With-Grain"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["Pro Plan Essentials"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.6,"bvReviewCount":3603,"conversionRate":35,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA DRY","manufacturerSku":"38100-13059","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOpt