3,2402,1756,1853,3279,1433,2288,1568,352,63,1716,1593,2344,1037,1759,2302,3035,654,1266,1881,1243,2717,1074,190,3262,2300,2314,2426,1846,1054,1110,531,293,1845,1941,1878,1286,2165,2310,737,1375,629,1089,1192,1640,1579,2781,2233,1221,1912,2471,1211,2331,144,2412,2188,2258,3020,2415,1945,2361,3274,2500,667,367,1742,671,2484,2066,1707,2248,2274,3011,1482,2230,443,1541,1240,765,2555,1487,105,1053,2232,1556,1650,409,634,2410,2327,1962,362,303,2235,55,2396,270,376,1700,1638,691,1521,389,3047,2425,2616,3180,3164,257,1097,2330,1051,2161,3021,2406,1994,2558,1747,304,3028,1220,739,2260,1101,2775,494,1488,2438,2160,208,2407,1828,2237,2724,83,1182,1084,1381,2422,2316,3133,2162,1354,387,1807,1601,335,1726,2149,2228,2385,441,2399,1167,2384,212,1416,276,1669,456,2492,1075,2442,550,2308,1725,622,2439,1524,2249,3077,639,2180,3010,547,3046,1705],"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":14.57,"cartonLength":7.48,"cartonWeight":11.46,"cartonWidth":16.14},"package":{"height":14.57,"length":7.48,"weight":11.46,"width":16.14},"brand":"Great Choice","customCategory":"Dog Pads","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e Count on Grreat Choice Dog Pads to control odors and give your pup a leak proof place to relieve himself indoors. These pads absorb up to three cups of urine and effectively control odors, keeping your home accident and odor free. Only at PetSmart. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eKey Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eAbsorbency of 2 cups\u003cli\u003eProtection duration of 8 hours\u003cli\u003eOdor neutralizer\u003cli\u003eLeakproof\u003cli\u003ePheromone Attractant\u003cli\u003eAdhesive Tabs\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e5270618\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003e Great Choice\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIncludes: \u003c/b\u003e Available in 10 Count, 50 Count and 150 Count sizes \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIntended Pet(s): \u003c/b\u003e Dogs; Also great for protecting crates and carriers \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor: \u003c/b\u003e White absorbent core; Blue protective cover \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eProduct Dimensions: \u003c/b\u003e Overall: 23 in L x 24 in W (58.4 x 60.9 cm); Core Dimensions: 20.86 in L x 21.65 in W \u003cbr\u003e \r\n\u003cb\u003eCapacity:\u003c/b\u003e Holds 2 cups \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eInstructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eStep 1: Select an area away from your dog\u0026#39;s food and bed. Unfold the pad and place it on the floor, tissue side up, poly side down. Secure with the adhesive tabs. \r\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eStep 2: Lead your dog to the pad to become accustomed to the scent and use. Repeat as needed until your dog is comfortable with using the pad.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eStep 3: Reward your dog for correctly using the pad. Dispose of the pad in a trash receptacle.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaution:\u003c/b\u003e \u003cbr\u003eDo not allow dog to eat or swallow dog pad. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNote:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Pads may be used under/around cat litter boxes, as well as with our training pad holders.","quantity":"150 Count","onlineFrom":1508025600000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store","Online"],"quantityDisplays":["100 Count and Over"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.3,"bvReviewCount":3194,"conversionRate":75,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"TIANJIN YIYI HYGIENE PRODUCTS","manufacturerSku":"PAD-03","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"737257755802","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":23.99,"strikethrough-number":3