:5.25,"cartonLength":16,"cartonWeight":28.25,"cartonWidth":13},"package":{"height":6,"length":18,"weight":28,"width":11.5},"brand":"World's Best","customCategory":"Litter","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter Multiple Cat Unscented formula harnesses the power of naturally absorbent corn with added natural plant ingredients for enhanced odor control to deliver 2 times longer lasting performance the leading US brand.  This naturally safe and sustainable formula is ideal for homes with 2 or more cats. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e \u003cli\u003eOUTSTANDING ODOR CONTROL - Multiple cats shouldn't mean more smells and more mess - keep your cats happy and house smelling clean with a natural litter with long-lasting odor control.\u003cli\u003e2.  QUICK CLUMPING \u0026 EASY SCOOPING - Tired of cleaning up after your cats?  Get the natural litter that's quick clumping, easy scooping and requires no chiseling or scraping.\r\n\u003cli\u003e3.  FLUSHABLE* - SEPTIC SAFE - Disposing of your litter just got easier.  Get the lightweight litter that\u0026#39;s tested and proven flushable* and safe for septic and sewer systems!\r\n\u003cli\u003e4.  LIGHTWEIGHT \u0026 99% DUST FREE - Using a lightweight cat litter with no clay dust means less mess.  Breathe easy with this natural litter made from whole-kernel corn.\u003cli\u003e5.  NATURALLY SAFE FOR YOU \u0026 YOUR CAT - Made from whole-kernel corn, this litter is naturally safe with no harmful chemicals, no artificial perfumes and no clay dust.\r\n \u003cli\u003e*Designed to flush in well-maintained systems.  Flush only 1-2 clumps of World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter at a time in the toilet.  The state of California encourages the disposal of cat feces in trash and discourages flushing feces in toilets or disposing of them in drains. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eMaterial:\u003c/b\u003e Whole-kernel corn\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eEnvironment Type:\u003c/b\u003e Litter Box\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eSpecies:\u003c/b\u003e Cat\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eClumping/Non-Clumping:\u003c/b\u003e Clumping\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor:\u003c/b\u003e Tan\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003ePackage Dimensions:\u003c/b\u003e 18 in H x 12 in W x 6.5 in D\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003ePackage Weight:\u003c/b\u003e 28 lb\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cb\u003eCleaning Instructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e1.  Transition slowly - Start with only a third of World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter added to a clean box of your current litter.  Then, once your cat is more familiar with it, change to two-thirds.  After that, use only World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter. 2.  Pick a good location - Provide at least one litter box per cat.  Place the box in a quiet place that can be easily accessed and is away from the cat\u0026#39;s food and water dishes. 3.  Keep it clean -For best results, scoop clumps daily and maintain a depth of 2-3 inches of World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaution:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003ePregnant or immune-suppressed persons should use good cleanliness and safety practices when handling soiled litter.  Cat feces can transmit a disease called toxoplasmosis.  Consult your physician for more information. World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter should be stored in a sealed bag or bin in an area that is cool, clean and dry. World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter should not be used as a traction aid on ice or snow. If your cat shows an adverse reaction or begins to eat the litter repeatedly, please discontinue use immediately and consult your veterinarian.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e1.  Start with a clean or new litter box, and mix one-third of World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter and two-thirds your current litter. 2.  When your cat is comfortable, change the proportion to two-thirds World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter.  3.  Make the switch complete and use only World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter. Maintain 2-3 inches of World\u0026#39;s Best Cat Litter.","onlineFrom":1388534400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"litter-features":["Clumping","Flushable","Lightweight","Low Dust","Multi-Cat","Unscented"],"litter-materials":["Corn"],"litter-types":["Natural"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.8,"bvReviewCount":7440,"conversionRate":60,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"KENT PET GROUP","manufacturerSku":"00612","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnlyOverride":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"322591006125","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":34.95,"strikethrough-number":42.69,"validUntil":"2035-01-01T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$34.95","strikethrough":"$42.69"},"displayType":"single"},"variations":["1 Size"],"categories":[[{"id":"500430","name":{"default":"Worlds Best"}},{"id":"5000000","name":{"default":"Featured Brands"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"60000060","name":{"default":"Curbside and In Store Pickup"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"200152","name":{"default":"Litter"}},{"id":"200211","name":{"default":"Litter and Waste Disposal"}},{"id":"200000","name":{"default":"Cat"}}],[{"id":"60080122","name":{"default":"Timezone Tes