h":24,"cartonWeight":30.4,"cartonWidth":19.5},"package":null,"brand":"Friskies","customCategory":"Dry Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003ePour a purr\u0026ndash;worthy dish full of yum with Purina Friskies Seafood Sensations dry cat food. Salmon, tuna and shrimp flavors combine to create a taste she'll love, and a touch of seaweed flavor balances out the recipe for delicious goodness. Essential vitamins and minerals in every serving let you feel good about offering this dry cat food to your feline friend, and the seafood flavors give her plenty of reasons to finish every last delectable bite. Each serving contains 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for every stage of life, so your cat can enjoy this scrumptious recipe from her playful kitten days all the way through her adventurous adult years. Let the sound of the delightful bites hitting her bowl send her prancing your way, and watch as she savors every bit of the ocean flavors. With so much goodness in every serving, she's sure to meow for more at mealtime.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eSeafood flavors for the taste cats love. 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for all life stages, Contains protein to support strong muscles. Tempting texture to please her palate, Essential fatty acids to help support healthy skin and coat. Vitamin A and taurine to help support clear, healthy vision, Formulated to meet industry standards for cat food. Checked for quality and safety, Proudly produced in our Purina\u0026ndash;owned U.S. facilities., Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5267332\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFriskies Seafood Sensations\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eKibble\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eWith Vitamins\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eMaintenance\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eSeafood\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e30.4 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eGround Yellow Corn, Corn Protein Meal, Poultry By\u0026ndash;Product Meal, Soybean Meal, Animal Fat Preserved With Mixed\u0026ndash;Tocopherols, Meat And Bone Meal, Liver Flavor, Ocean Fish Meal, Phosphoric Acid, Salt, Calcium Carbonate, Choline Chloride, Dehydrated Seaweed Meal, Salmon Meal, Shrimp Meal, Tuna Meal, MINERALS [Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite], Potassium Chloride, Dl\u0026ndash;Methionine, Taurine, VITAMINS [Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin A Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K)], L\u0026ndash;Tryptophan, Red 40, Blue 2, Yellow 5. K600323\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (Min)\u0026hellip;30.0%, Crude Fat (Min)\u0026hellip;11.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)\u0026hellip;3.0%, Moisture (Max)\u0026hellip;12.0%, Linoleic Acid (Min)\u0026hellip;1.2%, Arachidonic Acid (Min)\u0026hellip;0.02%, Calcium (Ca) (Min)\u0026hellip;1.0%, Phosphorus (P) (Min)\u0026hellip;0.9%, Zinc (Zn) (Min)\u0026hellip;125 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Selenium (Se) (Min)\u0026hellip;0.3 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin A (Min)\u0026hellip;10,000 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin E (Min)\u0026hellip;100 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Taurine (Min)\u0026hellip;0.12%\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e3,631 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 392 kcal\u0026frasl;cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeeding Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eUsing a standard 8 oz measuring cup. These amounts are averages and your cat's needs may differ. Feeding should be adjusted as necessary to maintain an ideal body condition. Want some variety? Serve it up by feeding your cat Friskies canned in addition to or mixed with Friskies dry. Remember, cats are nibblers who enjoy eating small meals throughout the day, so your cat would appreciate it if you keep a bowl of Friskies dry cat food available at all times. Keep in mind, pregnant and nursing cats may require 2 \u0026ndash; 4 times their normal feeding. LUCKY ENOUGH TO HAVE A KITTEN? Kittens generallynibble solid food at 3 \u0026ndash; 4 weeks of age. Keep moistened Friskies available to these kittens at all times. After weaning (at 6 \u0026ndash; 8 weeks of age), kittens will normally eat dry or moistened food at will. If water is added, use no more than one part warm (not hot) liquid to three parts Friskies, changing frequently to ensure freshness. CURIOUS ABOUT OTHER FRISKIES FLAVORS ?Remember, changes in your cat's diet should be made gradually to allow your cat to become accustomed to a new food. Substitute small amounts of the new food for the old food, gradually increasing the amount of the new food while decreasing the old food, over a period of 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets â something both you and your cat can appreciate. Provide adequate fresh water in a clean container daily. For your pet's health, see your veterinarian regularly.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eRemember, changes in your cat's diet should be made gradually to allow your cat to become accustomed to a new food. Substitute small amounts of the new food for the old food, gradually increasing the amount of the new food while decreasing the old food, over a period of 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets \r\n- something both you and your cat can appreciate.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCat\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Value Brands","onlineFrom":1501718400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"catLifestages":["Adult"],"environments":["Any"],"foodForms":["Bags"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"nutritionalOptions":["With-Grain"],"packagingTypes":["Bag"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.8,"bvReviewCount":11098,"conversionRate":75,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA DRY","manufacturerSku":"00-50000-96358","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"50000963584","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":27.48,"strikethrough-number":28.49,"validUntil":"2035-01-01T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$15.58-$27.48","strikethrough":"$17.29-$28.49"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["3 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"60080122","name":{"default":"Timezone Test"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"200172","name":{"default":"Dry Food"}},{"id":"200209","name":{"default":"Food and Treats"}},{"id":"200000","name":{"default":"Cat"}}],[{"id":"