1279,3180,2278,2255,570,668,1896,1382,1095,53,1415,2069,1192,1036,595,1062,516,2753,2272,2248,2484,2052,3102,2482,1486,1175,1296,1867,2779,2093,2426,1358,1835,2427,1212,737,3060,1928,3048,2298,1760,1841,130,2326,318,2246,2407,2447,281,2188,321,379,3046,3185,1590,2524,1058,1133,1334,2354,1581,1686,2703,461,1184,3157,1294,427,1197,3018,2280,3281,1636,729,2041,687,2778,2283,1551,2165,2289,137,1252,428,673,1626,1033,1541,436,1845,1223,1452,1813,1971,1891,1642,1099,1355,215,3133,1747,548,2324,521,294,1423,3068,3064,747,1208,247,50,2398,291,1081,1244,1650,2752,526,426,1953,1274,1508,1812,1793,1268,275,2391,594,2256,1145,2400,463,2473,1530,2525,429,1004,286,2264,290,1966,1442,1030,2390,287,1494,1353,575,2207,2363,779,1782,2344],"size":{"solidSize":"10 Oz"},"flavor":{"value":"Chicken \u0026 Rice","displays":"Chicken"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":3.19,"cartonLength":3,"cartonWeight":0.79,"cartonWidth":3},"package":null,"brand":"Simply Nourish","customCategory":"Canned Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eSimply Nourish Chicken \u0026amp; Rice Stew Dog Food is packed with carefully sourced animal proteins, superfoods and other naturally nutrient-rich ingredients. Our recipes simply have no room for fillers. Our nutritionists thoughtfully balance each recipe to help meet dogs' unique nutritional needs and support overall health. With flavors dogs love and formulas that feed their well-being, every food we create is designed to Simply Nourish. Only at PetSmart.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eKey Benefits:\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eReal chicken is the #1 ingredient\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eWholesome ingredients\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eShreds\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/b\u003e5286374\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/b\u003eSimply Nourish\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/b\u003eShreds\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/b\u003eChicken \u0026amp; Rice Recipe\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/b\u003e10 oz (283 g)\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNUTRITIONAL INFORMATION\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eChicken, Chicken Broth, Water Sufficient For Processing, Carrots, Tapioca Starch, Rice, Sunflower Oil, Calcium Lactate, Xanthan Gum, Tricalcium Phosphate, Calcium Carbonate, Zinc Sulfate, Choline Chloride, Vitamin E Supplement, Ferrous Sulfate, Calcium Pantothenate, Niacin, Thiamine Mononitrate, Vitamin A Supplement, Copper Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Riboflavin Supplement, Vitamin D3 Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Folic Acid, Potassium Iodide, Sodium Selenite, Vitamin B12 Supplement\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis:\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eCrude Protein (min) 10.0%\u003cbr /\u003eCrude Fat (min) 1.4%\u003cbr /\u003eCrude Fiber (max) 1.0%\u003cbr /\u003eMoisture (max) 83.0%\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content (ME Calculated): \u003c/b\u003e787 kcal/kg, 2,243 kcal/can\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFEEDING INSTRUCTIONS\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThe amount of food your dog requires will depend on activity, age, environment and breed. Feed at room temperature and refrigerate unused portion. Feed your dog 2 cans per 15 lbs of body weight per day. Always provide access to clean fresh water. Consult your veterinarian with any health questions.\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Natural","onlineFrom":1563148800000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodOuncesSizeDisplays":["8-15 Oz"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"nutritionalOptions":["Natural"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In St