1,2709,1104,1191,1117,1333,1386,1732,634,461,1308,2147,105,3169,2769,1627,1208,1335,3246,1307,446,685,3146,246,2487,56,3068,1526,86,252,1514,2313,379,495,774,2218,1011,1252,675,653,2492,2400,554,1601,1726,387,1300,82,1742,295,423,1614,1343,1762,2442,3165,413,97,1961,345,1185,1066,1864,594,1774,332,102,1414,3101,384,1933,1433,628,50,2705,3062,1032,74,3180,737,2760,1227,2089,504,1019,3040,1169,1334,454,453,3136,637,1436,1179,1259,2445,1128,2733,2702,300,1551,1808,1867,270,2196,1023,1372,3253,1720,1065,1678,2222,2402,2504,1303,1641,2749,2133,1562,1311,1037,2739,1148,1534,1243,429,3092,357,362,1830,1298,557,285,3010,129,1231,76,237,2211,1392,638,1506,548,2441,322,1942,1648,3073,2778,671,1434,208,242,321,3025,2493,1238,3082,2462,580,1339,2308,1853,391,2752,744,2722,3117,1364],"size":{"solidSize":"30 Oz"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":8.6,"cartonLength":3.4,"cartonWeight":2.17,"cartonWidth":2.3},"package":{"height":8.6,"length":3.4,"weight":2.17,"width":2.3},"brand":"Arm \u0026 Hammer","customCategory":"Deodorizers","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e The extra strength formula of ARM HAMMER Cat Litter Deodorizer Double Duty destroys feces and urine litter box odors on contact. Its moisture-activated scent refreshes every time your cat uses the litter box. In fact, internal lab tests demonstrate that it lowers odor levels after 9 days compared to clay, scoopable or natural - scented or unscented - cat litter alone. Use absorbent ARM HAMMER Cat Litter Deodorizer Double Duty regularly to help prevent litter clumps from sticking to the box. This cat litter deodorizer is safe for cats and owners to use every day when used as directed.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003e #1 CAT LITTER DEODORIZER BRAND* that\u0026#39;s formulated with ARM HAMMER Baking Soda Crystals to eliminate tough odors on contact. This cat litter deodorizer helps your litter box stay first-day fresh longer than cat litter alone.(*Based on units sold) \u003cli\u003e GET EXTRA STRENGTH ODOR ELIMINATION because this cat litter deodorizer\u0026#39;s extra strength formula destroys feces AND urine odors on contact. You\u0026#39;re left with a litter box that stays fresh every time you sprinkle in this cat litter deodorizer. \u003cli\u003e PROVEN ODOR CONTROL FOR 9 DAYS. Deodorize your litter box and enjoy that fresh, new-litter scent longer with this odor eliminator. In fact, internal lab tests demonstrate lower odor levels after 9 days compared to cat litter alone. \u003cli\u003e SAFE FOR DAILY USE AROUND CATS AND OWNERS. Its odor elimination comes from ARM \u0026 HAMMER Baking Soda Crystals, so you can safely sprinkle it in to deodorize your cat litter box every day when used as directed. \u003cli\u003e WORKS WITH ANY TYPE OF LITTER, whether you use cat litter that\u0026#39;s scented, unscented, clay, scoopable, or natural. Simply sprinkle in this absorbent litter deodorizer daily to deodorize your cat litter box\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eEnvironment Type:\u003c/b\u003e Litter Box\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eSpecies:\u003c/b\u003e Cats\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor:\u003c/b\u003e White\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003ePackage Weight:\u003c/b\u003e 30 oz (1 lb, 14 oz) 850 g\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eInstructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e1. In a clean, empty liter box, pour Arm \u0026 Hammer Double Duty Litter Deodorizer to cover the bottom of the litter box.\u003cbr\u003e2. Add any type of cat litter (clay, scoopable or natural) as usual.\u003cbr\u003e3. Sprinkle deodorizer on top of litter and mix it in.\u003cbr\u003e4. Between litter changes, repeat Step 3 to keep litter fresh.","onlineFrom":1521763200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.4,"bvReviewCount":1873,"conversionRate":120,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerNa