t\u0026#39;s so effective, millions have switched to Clump \u0026 Seal Cat Litter!\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003e 7-day guarantee. Experience the confidence of a 7-day odor free-home -guaranteed. \u003cli\u003e  99.9% Dust Free, No more dust clouds when pouring or scooping. \u003cli\u003e Seals and destroys odor. Moisture-activated Micro-Granules form a tight seal around cat waste odor, and heavy-duty odor eliminators plus ARM \u0026 HAMMER Baking Soda destroy sealed in odors on contact. \u003cli\u003e No crumbly clumps. Plant-derived particles help create rock solid clumps for easy scooping. \u003cli\u003e Strong enough for Multi-Cat households and also available in a Fresh Home Scent\u003cbr\u003e\r\n \r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eEnvironment Type:\u003c/b\u003e Indoors\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eSpecies:\u003c/b\u003e Cat\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003ePackage Weight:\u003c/b\u003e 38 lb\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCleaning Instructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFor best results, fill a clean, empty litter box with 3-4 inches of litter. Cat litter seals in and destroys odors, forming rock-solid clumps. Remove clumps and solid waste daily to keep the rest of the litter fresh. Add more cat litter to replace what you have scooped out and maintain a depth of 3-4 inches. For best results once a month, empty the entire litter box. Dispose of used kitty litter in trash. Do not flush or put in drains.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaution:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003ePlease wash hands thoroughly after handling used cat litter. We want to remind pregnant women and those with suppressed immune systems that a parasite sometimes found in cat feces can cause toxoplasmosis.","onlineFrom":1409011200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"litter-features":["Advanced Odor Control","Clumping","Low Dust","Low Tracking","Scented"],"litter-materials":["Clay"],"litter-types":["Clay"],"customPet":["Cat"],"produc