9,1029,2260,2264,82,435,339,494,629,300,1580,152,1517,1051,2148,2753,1637,3125,2441,126,1358,1181,1394,1938,99,3049,1361,2359,3262,415,3185,1773,1239,3096,2404,1307,3281,2275,1569,2440,3046,3005,245,2719,3280,1207,1497,2427,1458,2244,1762,1609,3029,1037,140,1262,87,1725,3068,3157,286,1624,310,2180,2385,3241,2412,1064,383,1814,349,479,1125,550,2233,220,1682,1867,2453,291,2347,401,595,583,3014,1731,1554,1438,2222,1579,2717,150,567,2560,289,1110,2737,2242,2630,2358,2113,3180,1229,2237,2207,2528,700,2093,2128,2271,2378,1004,1505,2722,2538,1651,1086,2215,1030,2395,1964,444,1167,270,634,1742,1163,2451,2431,3017,1526,3025,1119],"size":{"solidSize":"30 Count"},"flavor":{"value":"Variety","displays":"Other"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":7.6,"cartonLength":5.2,"cartonWeight":6.66,"cartonWidth":7.85},"package":null,"brand":"Fancy Feast","customCategory":"Canned Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eDelight your cat with a Purina Fancy Feast Poultry and Beef Classic Pate Cat Food Variety Pack. Crafted in partnership with our expert nutritionists, these protein\u0026ndash;rich, grain\u0026ndash;free cat food recipes feature the irresistible taste of real chicken, turkey, or beef as the number 1 ingredient and deliver 100 percent complete and balanced nourishment for adult cats. This high\u0026ndash;quality canned cat food variety pack includes formulas with a blend of vitamins and minerals to support your cat's whole body health and with a smooth cat food wet pate texture cat's love. These wet cat food pate recipes are made without artificial colors or preservatives, so you know your cat is getting everything they need and nothing they don't. Show your cat how much you care with the spellbinding aroma, smooth pate texture and delectable gourmet meal flavor they can't resist. Every Fancy Feast Classic Pate cat food is proudly manufactured and tested for quality and safety in Purina\u0026ndash;owned U.S. facilities.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eFancy Feast wet cat food made without artificial colors or preservatives. Crafted with real, high\u0026ndash;quality ingredients to deliver a 100 percent complete and balanced canned cat food for adult cats. Fancy Feast pate cat food developed in partnership with our expert nutritionists to create a unique and unforgettable taste experience for your cat. Canned cat food variety pack crafted with real chicken, turkey or beef as the number one ingredient with a smooth cat food wet pate texture. Protein\u0026ndash;rich, gourmet soft cat food recipe creates a flavor\u0026ndash;filled experience. Savory gravy adds to the delicious taste. Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5275858\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFancy Feast Pate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003ePate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAll Stages\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eNo Artificial Colors, No Artificial Preservatives, Real Meat, With Vitamins\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eMaintenance\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e6.66 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eClassic Pate Beef, Beef Broth, Meat By\u0026ndash;products, Liver, Fish, Artificial And Natural Flavors, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Guar Gum, Tricalcium Phosphate, Taurine, Salt, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate, Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin, Calcium Pantothenate, Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Riboflavin Supplement, Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin, Folic Acid, Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. D667920. Classic Pate Chicken Feast: Chicken, Chicken Broth, Meat By\u0026ndash;products, Liver, Fish, Artificial And Natural Flavors, Tricalcium Phosphate, Guar Gum, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, FerrousSulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Choline Chloride, Taurine, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement], Salt. E667222. Classic Pate Turkey \u0026#38; Giblets Feast: Turkey, Meat By\u0026ndash;products, Liver, Turkey Broth, Fish, Poultry Giblets, Artificial And Natural Flavors, Guar Gum, Tricalcium Phosphate, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Salt, Taurine, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. D668122\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eClassic Pate Tender Beef Feast: Crude Protein (Min)...11.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...4.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...1.5%, Moisture (Max)...78.0%, Ash (Max)...3.25%, Taurine (Min)...0.05% Classic Pate Chicken Feast: Crude Protein (Min)...10.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...5.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...1.5%, Moisture (Max)...78.0%, Ash (Max)...3.25%, Taurine (Min)...0.05% Classic Pate Turkey \u0026#38; Giblets Feast: Crude Protein (Min)...11.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...5.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...1.5%, Moisture (Max)...78.0%, Ash (Max)...3.25%, Taurine (Min)...0.05%\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003eTender Beef Feast: 1,087 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 92 kcal\u0026frasl;can; Classic Chicken Feast: 1,159 kcal\u0026frasl;kg 99 kcal\u0026frasl;can; ClassicTurkey \u0026#38; Giblets Feast: 1,124 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 96 kcal\u0026frasl;can\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeeding Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eFeed an average size adult cat 1 can per 3\u0026ndash;1\u0026frasl;2 pounds of body weight daily. Feed up to twice this amount to kittens. Pregnant or nursing cats may require 2\u0026ndash;4 times their normal feeding.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCat\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1508976000000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"catLifestages":["Adult"],"environments":["Any"],"foodOuncesSizeDisplays":["16 Oz and Over"],"foodTextures":["Pate"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"packagingTypes":["Variety Pack"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["FANCY FEAST MAINLINE","Purina Cat Food \u0026 Treats"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.8,"bvReviewCount":892,"conversionRate":100,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA WET","manufacturerSku":"00-50000-17087","shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnlyOverride":false,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":false,"upc":"50000170876","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":28.06,"strikethrough-number":28.9