4,3025,1662,1108,1967,2169,251,2611,643,203,196,2201,1516,2133,1045,2193,1352,2329,649,2044,299,3265,1072,1857,179,339,2294,3278,604,597,1263,737,1120,245,1805,228,1599,2463,1011,2708,1280,1276,1642,1854,1888,1255,371,2454,1593,1959,1483,1670,256,1752,2542,1298,1953,453,3024,2037,1411,349,1074,3274,2199,2730,197,1249,249,1452,548,648,1278,2619,3249,1211,2386,2316,1647,2364,1488,3290,190,135,575,1007,392,2482,3250,3180,2459,152,1344,1121,2265,2038,2232,98,356,377,1122,282,1232,2469,774,1416,3008,2276,174,3046,1550,411,59,1345,2436,504],"size":{"solidSize":"30 Count"},"flavor":{"value":"Variety","displays":"Other"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":7.6,"cartonLength":5.2,"cartonWeight":6.66,"cartonWidth":7.85},"package":{"height":7.6,"length":5.2,"weight":6.66,"width":7.85},"brand":"Fancy Feast","customCategory":"Canned Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eDelight your cat with an exceptional mealtime experience with a Purina Fancy Feast Gravy Lovers Poultry and Beef Gourmet Wet Cat Food Gravy Variety Pack. Crafted in partnership with our expert nutritionists, this protein\u0026ndash;rich, canned cat food variety pack features real Fancy Feast Gravy Lovers turkey, chicken and beef formulas and delivers 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for adult cats. This high\u0026ndash;quality cat food with gravy variety pack includes recipes with a blend of vitamins and minerals to support your cat's whole body health. These in gravy cat food recipes are made without artificial colors or preservatives, so your cat gets everything they need and nothing they don't. Show your cat how much you care with the spellbinding aroma and gourmet meal flavor they can't resist. Every Purina Fancy Feast cat food with gravy is thoughtfully crafted and tested for quality and safety in Purina\u0026ndash;owned U.S. facilities.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCat food with gravy, made without artificial colors or preservatives,.Purina Fancy Feast canned cat food variety pack crafted with real, high\u0026ndash;quality ingredients, like real poultry or beef, to deliver 100 percent complete and balanced food for adult cats. An irresistible, protein\u0026ndash;rich Fancy Feast Gravy Lovers cat food taste offering a gourmet turkey, chicken or beef cat food meal with an enticing aroma and a light, savory gravy. Developed in partnership with our expert nutritionists to create a unique and unforgettable Purina Fancy Feast wet cat food taste experience for your cat. Canned cat food crafted in our U.S. facilities and undergoes regular quality and safety checks, Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5237489\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFancy Feast Gravy Lovers\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eGravy\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage:\u003c/b\u003eAll Stages\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eNo Artificial Colors, No Artificial Preservatives, Real Meat, With Vitamins\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eMaintenance\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eTurkey, Chicken, Beef\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e6.66 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eGravy Lovers Turkey Feast In Roasted Turkey Flavor Gravy: Turkey Broth, Turkey, Wheat Gluten, Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Liver, Chicken, Corn Starch\u0026ndash;modified, Soy Flour, Glycine, Salt, Natural Flavor, Tricalcium Phosphate, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Taurine, Choline Chloride, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. D702422 Chicken Feast In Grilled Chicken Flavor Gravy: Chicken Broth, Chicken, Wheat Gluten, Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Liver, Fish, Corn Starch\u0026ndash;modified, Soy Flour, Glycine, Salt, Natural Flavor, Tricalcium Phosphate, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Taurine, Choline Chloride, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. D702122 Beef Feast In Roasted Beef Flavor Gravy: Beef Broth, Beef, Wheat Gluten, Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Liver, Fish, Corn Starch\u0026ndash;modified,Chicken, Soy Flour, Glycine, Salt, Natural Flavor, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Tricalcium Phosphate, Taurine, Choline Chloride, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. D702022\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eGravy Lovers Turkey Feast in Roasted Turkey Flavor Gravy: Crude Protein (Min)...9.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...2.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...1.5%, Moisture (Max)...82.0%, Ash (Max)...3.0%, Taurine (Min)...0.05% Chicken Feast in Grilled Chicken Flavor Gravy: Crude Protein (Min)...9.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...2.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...1.5%, Moisture (Max)...82.0%, Ash (Max)...3.0%, Taurine (Min)...0.05% Beef Feast in Roasted Beef Flavor Gravy: Crude Protein (Min)...9.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...2.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...1.5%, Moisture (Max)...82.0%, Ash (Max)...3.0%, Taurine (Min)...0.05%\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003eTurkey Feast: 774 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 65 kcal\u0026frasl;can; Chicken Feast: 798 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 67 kcal\u0026frasl;can; Beef Feast: 775 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 65 kcal\u0026frasl;can\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeeding Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eTurkey Feast: Feed an average size adult cat 1 can per 2\u0026ndash;1\u0026frasl;2 pounds of body weight daily. Chicken Feast: Feed an average size adult cat 1 can per 2\u0026ndash;1\u0026frasl;2 pounds of body weight daily. Beef Feast: Feed an average size adult cat 1 can per 2\u0026ndash;1\u0026frasl;2 pounds of body weight daily. Feed up to twice this amount to kittens.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCat\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1433808000000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"catLifestages":["All Life Stages"],"environments":["Any"],"foodOuncesSizeDisplays":["16 Oz and Over"],"foodTextures":["In Gravy"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"packagingTypes":["Variety Pack"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["FANCY FEAST MAINLINE