,3153,1296,2481,1035,164,1191,367,308,1381,2216,55,1431,1838,381,288,1570,3016,191,1689,2363,642,3049],"size":{"solidSize":"34 Lb"},"flavor":{"value":"Salmon \u0026 Rice","displays":"Fish, Salmon"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":4.75,"cartonLength":31,"cartonWeight":34.4,"cartonWidth":16},"package":{"height":31,"length":4.75,"weight":34,"width":16},"brand":"Purina Pro Plan","customCategory":"Dry Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e Serve your dog nutrition that performs with Purina Pro Plan Large Breed Sensitive Skin and Stomach Salmon and Rice adult dry dog food. With real salmon as the first ingredient, this high protein dog food delivers savory flavor to capture your dog\u0026#39;s attention. Oat meal is gentle on his digestive system, while antioxidants provide immune support. Also included are fish oil for dogs with dog omega 3 fatty acids, DHA and EPA, and glucosamine for joint health and mobility, while omega 6 for dogs supports their healthy skin and lustrous coat. Purina formulates this product with natural prebiotic fiber to nourish specific intestinal bacteria for digestive health. This wheat-free and soy-free recipe is made without artificial colors or flavors. Offer 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition to your dog with Purina Pro Plan Large Breed Sensitive Skin and Stomach Salmon and Rice adult dry dog food.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eKey Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eHigh protein dog food promotingmuscle conditioning when combined with proper exercise   and featuring salmon is the first ingredient and fish oil sources of EPA for heart health\u003cli\u003e Dog kibble featuring glucosamine and EPA, an omega-3 fatty acid, for joint health and mobility and 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for large adult dogs\u003cli\u003e Sensitive skin dog food with omega-6 fatty acids to nourish healthy skin and lustrous coat\u003cli\u003e Dog food for sensitive stomachs that\u0026#39;s gentle on the stomach to maintain stool quality, including natural prebiotic fiber to nourish specific intestinal bacteria and easily digestible oat meal\u003cli\u003e Veterinarian recommended Purina Pro Plan salmon dog food for large breeds contains antioxidants for a healthy immune system \u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePro Plan Sensitive Skin \u0026#38; Stomach Formula\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eCrunchy, Kibble\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eLarge Breed\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCorn Free, No Artificial Colors, No Artificial Flavors, Potato Free, Soy Free, Wheat Free, High\u0026ndash;Protein, Real Meat, Omegas, Prebiotic, Probiotics\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eDigestive Health, Bone Health, Maintenance, Non\u0026ndash;Prescription, Sensitive Skin, Sensitive Stomach, Skin \u0026#38; Coat, Energy \u0026#38; Vitality Support, Hip \u0026#38; Joint Support, Immune Support, Muscle Support\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eFish, Salmon\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e34.4 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eSalmon, Rice, Barley, Oat Meal, Fish Meal, Canola Meal, Salmon Meal, Beef Fat Preserved With Mixed\u0026ndash;Tocopherols, Dried Yeast, Natural Flavor, Sunflower Oil, Dried Chicory Root, Salt, Fish Oil, Calcium Carbonate, Potassium Chloride, Vitamins [Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Vitamin A Supplement, Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement], L\u0026ndash;Lysine Monohydrochloride, Taurine, Minerals [Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite], Choline Chloride, Dl\u0026ndash;Methionine, Potassium Citrate, Glucosamine Hydrochloride, L\u0026ndash;Ascorbyl\u0026ndash;2\u0026ndash;Polyphosphate (Vitamin C). B447522\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (Min)...26.0%, Crude Fat (Min)...12.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)...4.5%, Moisture (Max)...12.0%, Linoleic Acid (Min)...1.5%, Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) (Min)...0.12%, Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA) (Min)...0.12%, Calcium (Ca) (Min)...1.0%, Phosphorus (P) (Min)...0.8%, Selenium (Se) (Min)...0.35 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin A (Min)...15,000 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin E (Min)...460 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C)* (Min)...70 mg\u0026frasl;kg Total Glucosamine* (Min)...500 ppm, Glucosamine Hydrochloride* (Max)...520 ppm, Omega\u0026ndash;3 Fatty Acids* (Min)...0.65%, Omega\u0026ndash;6 Fatty Acids* (Min)...1.6%, *Not recognized as an essential nutrient by the AAFCO Dog Food Nutrient Profiles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e3,567 kcal/kg, 404 kcal/cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eMAKING THE SWITCH TO PRO PLAN Although you\u0026#39;ll be anxious to see the difference Pro Plan can make in your dog, please allow 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days to ease the transition from your dog\u0026#39;s current food. Each day, simply feed a little less of the previous food and a little more Pro Plan until you\u0026#39;re feeding Pro Plan exclusively. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eDog\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1693612800000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthCo