ors. Designed with SwiftDry Technology, they quickly turn liquid into gel to help prevent tracking. Adhesive tabs help hold the pad in place, while a pheromone attractant encourages instinctive marking. \r\n \r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures: \u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eLeakproof with adhesive tabs\u003cli\u003eOdor neutralizer\u003cli\u003ePheromone Attractant \u003cli\u003eBigger and more absorbent than previous Top Paw X-Large Dog Pads\u003cli\u003eHolds 8 cups\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIncludes: \u003c/b\u003e 150 Count\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIntended Pet(s): \u003c/b\u003e Dogs \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor: \u003c/b\u003e White\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eDimensions:\u003c/b\u003e 28 in L x 34 in W (71.1 x 86.3 cm)\u003cbr\u003e\r\n \r\n\u003cb\u003eCaution:\u003c/b\u003e Do not allow dog to eat or swallow dog pad.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eDirections:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e \r\n1. Select an area away from your dog's food and bed. Unfold the pad and place it on the floor, tissue side up, poly side down. Secure with adhesive tabs.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n2. Lead your dog tothe pad to become accustomed to its scent and use. Repeat as needed until your dog is comfortable using the pad.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n3. Reward your dog for correctly using the pad. Dispose of the pad in a trash receptacle.","quantity":"150 Count","onlineFrom":1517875200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"quantityDisplays":["100 Count and Over"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.6,"bvReviewCount":289,"conversionRate":105,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"TIANJIN YIYI HYGIENE PRODUCTS","manufacturerSku":"TP XL 150CT-2","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligibl