splays":"Lamb"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":4.5,"cartonLength":23,"cartonWeight":24.3,"cartonWidth":16},"package":{"height":4.1,"length":22.9,"weight":23.76,"width":15.2},"brand":"Purina Pro Plan","customCategory":"Dry Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eCare for your dog's sensitive skin and stomach while still tending to his nutritional needs with Purina Pro Plan Sensitive Skin and Sensitive Stomach Lamb and Oat Meal Formula adult dry dog food. This dog kibble is made with fish oil, a source of EPA and DHA for heart health, plus a wealth of other wholesome ingredients you expect from a super\u0026ndash;premium sensitive skin dog food. Also included are omega 6 for dogs and vitamin A in every serving to nourish your dog's skin and promote his healthy coat so he can look his very best. Your dog will also get omega\u0026ndash;3 fatty acids for healthy joints and mobility to help support his active lifestyle. With high\u0026ndash;quality ingredients chosen for a specific nutritional or functional purpose, this dog food for sensitive stomachs delivers outstanding nutrition to your best buddy's bowl every day. Make this Purina Pro Plan lamb dog food with oat meal a part of his regular diet and show him just how important his overall health and wellness are to you.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eHigh protein dog food featuring real lamb as number one ingredient, plus oat meal which is easily digestible and gentle on the digestive system. High in omega 6 for dogs to support healthy skin and a lustrous coat. Veterinarian recommended Purina Pro Plan lamb dog food with prebiotic fiber to nourish specific intestinal bacteria for digestive health. Rich in antioxidants for a healthy immune system and fish for dogs oil rich in omega\u0026ndash;3 fatty acids for joint health and mobility, plus EPA and DHA for heart health. Sensitive dry dog food that's gentle on the stomach to maintain stool quality and made without artificial colors, flavors or poultry by\u0026ndash;product meal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePro Plan Sensitive Skin \u0026#38; Stomach Formula\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eKibble\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCorn Free, No Artificial Colors, No Artificial Flavors, Potato Free, Wheat Free, Soy Free, High\u0026ndash;Protein, Real Meat, With Vitamins, Omegas, Prebiotic\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eBone Health, Brain Development, Digestive Health, Sensitive Skin, Sensitive Stomach, Skin \u0026#38; Coat, Veterinarian Recommended, Energy \u0026#38; Vitality Support, Heart Health, Immune Support, Muscle Support\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eLamb\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e16.25 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eLamb, Oat Meal, Barley, Fish Meal, Canola Meal, Rice, Beef Fat Preserved With Mixed\u0026ndash;Tocopherols, Dried Egg Product, Pea Protein, Dried Yeast, Natural Flavor, Fish Oil, Sunflower Oil, Dried Chicory Root, Calcium Carbonate, Salt, L\u0026ndash;Lysine Monohydrochloride, Potassium Chloride, Vitamins [Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Vitamin A Supplement, Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7)], Minerals [Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite], Choline Chloride, L\u0026ndash;Ascorbyl\u0026ndash;2\u0026ndash;Polyphosphate (Vitamin C). C445322\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (Min)\u0026hellip;26.0%, Crude Fat (Min)\u0026hellip;16.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)\u0026hellip;4.0%, Moisture (Max)\u0026hellip;12.0%, Linoleic Acid (Min)\u0026hellip;1.3%, Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) (Min)\u0026hellip;0.1%, Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA) (Min)\u0026hellip;0.1%, Calcium (Ca) (Min)\u0026hellip;1.0%, Phosphorus (P) (Min)\u0026hellip;0.8%, Selenium (Se) (Min)\u0026hellip;0.35 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin A (Min)\u0026hellip;15,000 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin E (Min)\u0026hellip;460 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C)* (Min)\u0026hellip;70 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Glucosamine* (Min)\u0026hellip;400 ppm, Omega\u0026ndash;3 Fatty Acids* (Min)\u0026hellip;0.7%, Omega\u0026ndash;6 Fatty Acids* (Min)\u0026hellip;1.5%, *Not recognized as an essential nutrient by the AAFCO Dog Food Nutrient Profiles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e3926 kcal/kg, 528 kcal/cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eMAKING THE SWITCH TO PRO PLAN Although you\u0026#39;ll be anxious to see the difference Pro Plan can make in your dog, please allow 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days to ease the transition from your dog\u0026#39;s current food. Each day, simply feed a little less of the previous food and a little more Pro Plan until you\u0026#39;re feeding Pro Plan exclusively. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eDog\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Specialized Nutrition","onlineFrom":1464998400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodForms":["Bags"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["Sensitive Skin","Sensitive Stomach"],"kibbleSizes":["Medium Breed"],"nutritionalOptions":["Wit