g food is science-backed nutrition that is specially formulated to nourish healthy pets who are prone to occasional digestive upsets and support healthy skin. This highly digestible formula for sensitive stomachs uses prebiotic fiber to fuel gut bacteria and support a balanced microbiome. In addition, this dry dog food is made with natural ingredients with added vitamins, minerals and amino acids. This food is an excellent source of vitamin E and Omega-6 fatty acids to nourish the dog\u0026#39;s skin, and help maintain a healthy, shiny coat. This food is packed with a powerful combination of clinically proven antioxidants, including vitamins C and E, to support a healthy immune system. This nutrition is formulated with decades of cutting-edge research to be a great-tasting meal for adult dogs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eHighly digestible formula with prebiotic fiber that is gentle on the stomach for optimal nutrient absorption\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eEnriched with Vitamin E and Omega-3 \u0026#38; 6 fatty acids, for healthy skin and a lustrous coat\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eClinically proven antioxidants, Vitamin C+E, for a healthy immune system\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003e27 key nutrients, including essential vitamins, minerals, and omega 3 \u0026#38; 6 fatty acids. Complete and balanced nutrition for adult dogs\u0026#39; health\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eHigh quality chicken is the #1 ingredient\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eMade with natural ingredients with added vitamins, minerals and amino acids\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eMade in the USA with Global Ingredients you can trust\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli\u003eHill\u0026#39;s Pet Nutrition is the US Veterinarians\u0026#39; #1 recommended brand\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCanine\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eScience Diet\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eKibble\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eCanine|Adult 11+|Medium breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eLarge Breed\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eHill\u0026#39;s Science Diet Adult Sensitive Stomach \u0026#38; Skin Chicken Recipe dry dog food is science-backed nutrition tailored for skin and digestive health, packed with clinically proven, immune system supporting antioxidants.- Highly digestible formula with prebiotic fiber that is gentle on the stomach for optimal nutrient absorption- Enriched with Vitamin E and Omega-3 \u0026#38; 6 fatty acids, for healthy skin and a lustrous coat- Clinically proven antioxidants, vitamin C+E, for a healthy immune system\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eDigestive Care, Food Sensitivities, Skin Care\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eChicken\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e13.605 KG \r\n/ 30.000 LB\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eChicken, Chicken Meal, Yellow Peas, Cracked Pearled Barley, Brown Rice, Brewers Rice, Whole Grain Sorghum, Egg Product, Chicken Fat, Soybean Oil, Dried Beet Pulp, Chicken Liver Flavor, Lactic Acid, Flaxseed, Pork Liver Flavor, Potassium Chloride, Iodized Salt, vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, L-Ascorbyl-2-Polyphosphate (source of Vitamin C), Niacin Supplement, Thiamine Mononitrate, Vitamin A Supplement, Calcium Pantothenate, Riboflavin Supplement, Biotin, Vitamin B12 Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Folic Acid, Vitamin D3 Supplement), Choline Chloride, Taurine, Mixed Tocopherols for freshness, minerals (Ferrous Sulfate, Zinc Oxide, Copper Sulfate, Manganous Oxide, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite), Natural Flavors, Beta-Carotene.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e391\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eNutrient GA Min GA Max Moisture 10.0 %, Protein 20.0 %, Fat 13.0 %, Crude Fiber 4.0 %, Ash 7.5 %, Vitamin C 85.0 ppm, Vitamin E 400.0 IU/kg, Total Omega-3 FA 0.3 %, Total Omega-6 FA 2.5 %\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeeding Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eThese amounts are a starting point only and should be adjusted to maintain proper weight. When feeding this food for the first time, mix increasing amounts of the pet\u0026#39;s new food with decreasing amounts of the old food over a 7-day period.\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Specialized Nutrition","onlineFrom":1370995200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodForms":["Bags"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["Sensitive Stomach"],"kibbleSizes":["Large Breed","Medium Breed"],"nutritionalOptions":["With-Grain"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["Paws for Pet Health"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.6,"bvReviewCount":2060,"conversionRate":35,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"HILLS PET NUTRITION, INC.","manufacturerSku":"8839","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"52742883908","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":89.99,"strikethrough-number":96.99,"validUntil":"2026-03-23T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$23.99-$104.99","strikethrough":"$24.99-$117.49"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["4 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"S03-Dog","name":{"default":"Dog Sale"}},{"id":"S03","name":{"default":"March"}},{"id"