293,789,304,1197,1007,2231,596,1476,2237,367,2710,3086,1521,1099,1641,1338,2248,1580,2439,1350,1881,526,3235,1010,3309,267,2233,1712,1054,334,3021,2328,539,457,398,2526,1342,232,1640,635,2302,2113,2280,633,1372,2706,1416,1132,1921,1826,417,2430,1194,1577,2213,2264,221],"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":15.35,"cartonLength":8.27,"cartonWeight":14.77,"cartonWidth":16.73},"package":null,"brand":"Great Choice","customCategory":"Dog Pads","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eCount on Grreat Choice Dog Pads to control odors and give your pup a leak proof place to relieve himself indoors. These extra-large pads absorb up to three cups of urine and effectively control odors, keeping your home accident and odor free. Only at PetSmart. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eInstructions:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nStep 1: Select an area away from your dog\u0026#39;s food and bed. Unfold the pad and place it on the floor, tissue side up, poly side down. Secure with the adhesive tabs. \u003cbr\u003eStep 2: Lead your dog to the pad to become accustomed to the scent and use. Repeat as needed until your dog is comfortable with using the pad.\u003cbr\u003eStep 3: Reward your dog for correctly using the pad. Dispose of the pad in a trash receptacle.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures: \u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eAbsorbency of 3 cups\u003cli\u003eProtect duration of 10 hours\u003cli\u003eOdor neutralizer\u003cli\u003eLeak proof\u003cli\u003ePheromone Attractant\u003cli\u003eAdhesive Tabs\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIncludes: \u003c/b\u003eAvailable in 10 Count, 50 Count and 150 Count Sizes\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIntended Pet(s): \u003c/b\u003eDogs; Also great for protecting crates and carriers \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor: \u003c/b\u003e White absorbent core; Blue protective cover\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eProduct Dimensions: \u003c/b\u003e Overall: 28 in L x 30 in W (71.1 x 76.2 cm); Core Dimensions: 23.62 in L x 27.55 in W\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eCapacity: \u003c/b\u003e Holds 3 cups\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eCaution: \u003c/b\u003e Do not allow dog to eat or swallow dog pad.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNote:\u003c/b\u003e Pads may be used under/around cat/litter boxes, as well as with training pad holders. \u003cbr\u003e","quantity":"150 Count","onlineFrom":1508025600000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"quantityDisplays":["100 Count and Over"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.2,"bvReviewCount":2337,"conversionRate":90,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"TIANJIN YIYI HYGIENE PRODUCTS","manufacturerSku":"PAD-06","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"737257755840","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":44.99,"strikethrough-number":null,"validUntil":"","formatted":{"primary":"$44.99"},"displayType":"single"},"variations":["1 Size"],"categories":[[{"id":"S03-Dog","name":{"default":"Dog Sale"}},{"id":"S03","name":{"default":"March"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"100262","name":{"default":"Potty Training"}},{"id":"100412","name":{"default":"Training and Behavior"}},{"id":"100000","name":{"default":"Dog"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"5000265","name":{"default":"Great Choice"}},{"id":"5000000","name":{"default":"Featured Brands"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"AFD-