e your dog with the high-quality protein that helps him thrive. A combination of hard kibble and tender shredded pieces serves up a satisfying texture, while the salmon and rice flavor caters to your canine's cravings. \r\n\r\n\u003cb\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\nFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e Salmon as the first ingredient for a good source of protein; wheat bran supplies natural prebiotic fibers to facilitate good digestive function; vitamin A and linoleic acid nourish skin and coat; antioxidants help build a strong immune system; hard kibble and tender shredded pieces deliver irresistible taste and texture.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePro Plan Complete Essentials\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eCrunchy, Hard, Kibble, Semi\u0026ndash;Moist, Shredded\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eCarrageenan Free, No Artificial Colors, No Artificial Flavors, Potato Free, High\u0026ndash;Protein, Real Meat, With Vitamins, High Fiber, Omegas, Prebiotic, Probiotics\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eAppetite Support, Gastrointestinal, Digestive Health, Immune Support, Hip \u0026#38; Joint Support, Muscle Support, Bone Health, Dental, Energy \u0026#38; Vitality Support, Eye Health\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eSalmon\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e34.4 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eSalmon, Rice, Whole Grain Wheat, Poultry By\u0026ndash;Product Meal, Whole Grain Corn, Soybean Meal, Beef Fat Preserved With Mixed\u0026ndash;Tocopherols, Corn Protein Meal, Fish Meal, Natural Flavor, Dried Beet Pulp, Dried Egg Product, Glycerin, Mono And Dicalcium Phosphate, Wheat Bran, Calcium Carbonate, Soybean Oil, Salt, Potassium Chloride, Minerals [Zinc Proteinate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Proteinate, Copper Proteinate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite], Vitamins [Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B3), Vitamin A Supplement, Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement], Choline Chloride, Dried Bacillus Coagulans Fermentation Product, L\u0026ndash;Ascorbyl\u0026ndash;2\u0026ndash;Polyphosphate (Vitamin C), L\u0026ndash;Lysine Monohydrochloride, Garlic Oil. E449223\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (min)\u0026hellip;26.0%, Crude Fat (min)\u0026hellip;16.0%, Crude Fiber (max)\u0026hellip;3.0%, Moisture (max)\u0026hellip;12.0%, Linoleic Acid (min)\u0026hellip; 1.4%, Calcium (Ca) (min)\u0026hellip; 1.0%, Phosphorus (P)(min)\u0026hellip; 0.8%, Selenium (Se) (min)\u0026hellip; 0.35 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin A (min)\u0026hellip; 15000 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Vitamin E (min)\u0026hellip; 460 IU\u0026frasl;kg, Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) (min)*\u0026hellip;70 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Glucosamine (min)*\u0026hellip;400 mg\u0026frasl;kg, Omega\u0026ndash;6 fatty acid (min)*\u0026hellip; 1.5%, Bacillus Coagulans (min)*\u0026hellip;600 million cfu\u0026frasl;lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e3856 kcal\u0026frasl;kg389 kcal/cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eMAKING THE SWITCH TO PRO PLAN Although you'll be anxious to see the difference Pro Plan can make in your dog, please allow 7 \u0026ndash; 10 days to ease the transition from your dog's current food. Each day, simply feed a little less of the previous food and a little more Pro Plan until you're feeding Pro Plan exclusively. This gradual transition will help avoid dietary upsets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eDog\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Specialized Nutrition","onlineFrom":1394150400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodForms":["Bags"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"kibbleSizes":["Large Breed","Medium Breed"],"nutritionalOptions":["With-Grain"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["Pro Plan Essentials"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.7,"bvReviewCount":1660,"conversionRate":60,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA DRY","manufacturerSku":"81001-60546","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"38100160546","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":74.48,"strikethrough-number":null,"validUntil":"","formatted":{"primary":"$16.58-$74.48"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["3 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"S03-Dog","name":{"default":"Dog Sale"}},{"id":"S03","name":{"default":"March"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"5000085","name":{"default":"Dog"}},{"id":"5000083","name":{"default":"Purina Pro Plan"}},{"id":"5000000","name":{"default":"Featured Brands"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"S03Dog-10X","name":{"default":"10x Dog Large Food Bags"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6