,1215,2464,83,1166,3046,81,1004,2581,2567,600,2448,135,100,1106,580,2771,385,2526,3133,651,53,3087,1187,1951,3021,1579,1562,1796,1050,247,2703,1148,2422,71,715,1181,1183,2349,3001,241,391,1198,3062,2310,2572,253,1266,252,3060,1975,1505,1774,1269,2439,300,3280,1413,3122,3080,1221,2291,3194,2475,3107,1130,1014,1843,1840,643,1290,2487,1365,1414,2743,2503,130,2237,672,724,2723,638,1515,2384,1618,1082,1267,2754,373,3277,2770,1574,2188,1144,1145,3274,2309,1335,1683,1230,1248,421,646,1513,2186,3279,2378,173,2275,2223,2334,2160,3246,399,1718,426,3273,1631,1866,394,1970,1039,1522,2391,2179,1125,1353,1661,550,2458,1680,320,70,1751,1558,1231,1385,389,390,230,3205,3164,2760,1532,1309,376,334,2264,2246,1851,3099,3069,1461,523,1933,2372,324,593,2286,3008,60,1752,2361,2389,493,1209,1733,293,1045,1841,1175,123,381,1238,408,1040,2147,1038,154,2440,1994,2449,2481,2447,435,1614,3047,1236,748,1262,1074,1296,257,87,1263,788,1652,1526,1072,248,174,1516,416,1058,2479,463,1357,1498,2258,1806,1401,1793,1714,3234],"size":{"solidSize":"30 Lb"},"flavor":{"value":"Lamb \u0026 Oatmeal","displays":"Lamb"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":5.51,"cartonLength":29.92,"cartonWeight":30.32,"cartonWidth":15.75},"package":{"height":5.8,"length":23.2,"weight":30.05,"width":15.7},"brand":"Simply Nourish","customCategory":"Dry Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e Simply Nourish Adult Lamb \u0026amp; Oatmeal Recipe Dry Dog Food includes a blend of superfoods like kale, pumpkin, blueberries and other naturally nutritious ingredients. Each ingredient is chosen for its role in supporting skin \u0026 coat, digestion and overall health.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eKey Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eDeboned lamb is the #1 ingredient\u003cli\u003eMade with whole grains\u003cli\u003eFree of colors, flavors or preservatives \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5287507\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003e Simply Nourish\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003e Dry\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration:\u003c/b\u003e Skin \u0026 Coat, Digestion\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003e Adult\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eFlavor:\u003c/b\u003e Lamb \u0026 Oatmeal Recipe\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eWeight:\u003c/b\u003e 30 lb (13.6 kg); 60 cups per bag\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNUTRITIONAL INFORMATION\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e    \r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eDeboned Lamb, Oatmeal, Brown Rice, Turkey Meal, Lamb Meal, Barley, Canola Oil (Preserved with Mixed Tocopherols), Natural Flavor, Pea Fiber, Whole Flaxseed, Sunflower Oil (Preserved with Mixed Tocopherols), Potassium Chloride, Dried Chicory Root, Dried Carrots, Dried Kale, Dried Pumpkin, Dried Blueberries, Choline Chloride, Minerals (Zinc Sulfate, Zinc Proteinate, Iron Proteinate, Ferrous Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Copper Proteinate, Manganese Sulfate, Sodium Selenite, Manganese Proteinate), Vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, Vitamin A Supplement, Niacin Supplement, d-Calcium Pantothenate, Riboflavin Supplement, Thiamine Mononitrate, Biotin, Vitamin B12 Supplement,\r\nPyridoxine Hydrochloride, Calcium Iodate, Folic Acid, Vitamin D3 Supplement), DL-Methionine, Taurine, Citric Acid (A Preservative), Mixed Tocopherols (A Preservative), Rosemary Extract\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCrude Protein (min) 25.0%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eCrude Fat (min) 13.0%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eCrude Fiber (max) 5.0%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eMoisture (max) 10.0%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eCalcium (min) 1.6 %\r\n\u003cbr\u003ePhosphorus (min) 1.0%\r\n\u003cbr\u003ePotassium (min) 0.6%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eZinc (min) 175 mg/kg\r\n\u003cbr\u003eSelenium (min) 0.35 mg/kg\r\n\u003cbr\u003eVitamin A (min) 20,000 IU/kg\r\n\u003cbr\u003eVitamin E (min) 200 IU/kg\r\n\u003cbr\u003eOmega-6 Fatty Acids* (min) 1.8%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eOmega-3 Fatty Acids* (min) 0.7%\u003cbr\u003e*Not recognized as an essential nutrient by the AAFCO Cat Food Nutrient Profiles.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e 3,405 kcal/kg, 355 kcal/cup\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFEEDING INSTRUCTIONS\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFor adult dogs, feed Simply Nourish Lamb \u0026 Oatmeal Recipe Adult Dog Food either dry or moistened with water. Begin with the recommendations provided and adjust to maintain body weight. Dogs may be fed once or twice per day.\u003cbr\u003e \u003cp\u003eWater: Provide your dog with fresh water in a clean container daily.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlways consult your veterinarian with any health questions. Wash hands with soap and warm water after handling.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eToy dog 3-12 lb: 1/2-1-1/4 cups daily\u003cbr\u003eSmall dog 13-20 lb: 1-1/4-1-3/4 cups daily\u003cbr\u003eMedium dog 21-50 lb: 1-3/4-3-1/2 cups daily\u003cbr\u003eLarge dog 51-90 lb: 3-1/2-5-1/2 cups daily\u003cbr\u003eExtra-large dog 90+ lb: 5-1/2 cups + 1/2 cup for each 10 lb of body weight over 90 lb\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTransition Instructions\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Whenever there is a change to a pet\u0026#39s food, it is important\r\nto make the change gradually. Mix a small amount of the new food with the current food and gradually increase the new food over the course of a week.","foodCategory":"Natural","onlineFrom":1562544000000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["Adult"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"kibbleSizes":["All Breeds"],"nutritionalOptions":["Natural","With-Grain"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["Simply Nourish Original"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.5,"bvReviewCount":685,"conversionRate":65,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"DIAMOND PET FOODS",