,3123,1589,278,1757,1071,2123,1234,352,453,2423,3133,96,269,1300,2358,271,1163,1953,245,1169,1081,725,687,1731,408,1793,3268,633,2730,232,1565,1038,3160,1196,2559,1473,1309,467,635,479,502,694,1356,1867,2521,1843,2424,2402,2560,2230,1503,1189,392,3097,292,2203,1102,1725,400,1298,319,309,629,3253,1180,2761,1127,2440,1049,1229,577,1217,1086,2302,198,2474,305,1041,3131,2349,128,3256,1556,1265,1182,650,3178,1483,2304,1072,295,2046,1296,257,2775,1971,1505,2503,648,1752,172,356,1225,2160,1328,1442,651,230,1183,1751,322,1822,1030,2298,454,1678,418,248,1700,1037,507,1015,1053,534,554,1346,2443,774,747,2527,1740,1194,2330,385,653,1153,2228,1341,81,514,1294,1354,1286,2700,357,2482,3062,1006,1266,3055,572,1525,576,670,1650,3046,411,1637,241,779,291,1661,3149,441,2445,1386,595,1115],"size":{"threeDimensionalSize":"42\"L x 28\"W x 30\"H"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":43.98,"cartonLength":3.94,"cartonWeight":34.65,"cartonWidth":29.53},"package":{"height":4,"length":44,"weight":34.7,"width":30},"brand":"Top Paw","customCategory":"Crates","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eCreate a safe and customizable home for your dog with the Top Paw\u0026reg; Double-Door Folding Crate. A crate is your pet\u0026#39;s home, den, and comfort zone. It\u0026#39;s where they can go to find security and to feel safe. Two doors are included for added convenience and versatility, while a divider panel lets you customize the crate space as your dog grows. Once your dog is fully grown, remove the divider panel. Additionally, it\u0026#39;s a helpful tool for potty training, enabling you to section off a sleep area that your dog will instinctively want to keep clean. Along with the ability to fold the crate flat for easy storage, a detachable handle is included for hassle-free storage. With additional features like slide-bolt latches for easy locking and unlocking, plus rubber feet to protect your floors, we\u0026#39;ve thought through form and function so your pet can focus on feeling comfy, secure, and right at home. Crate mats are sold separately. Exclusively at PetSmart.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003e Double-Door 42\u0026quot; Folding Crate for dogs that are up to \r\n27\u0026quot; tall and 40\u0026quot; \r\nlong\u003cli\u003e If your dog is on the higher side of these dimensions, we recommend choosing a larger crate for maximum comfort\u0026mdash;when in doubt, size up\u003cli\u003e Two doors for added convenience and versatility, making placement and access easier in any space\u003cli\u003e Features an easy-to-clean, leak-proof pan and a convenient divider panel to adjust the space as your dog grows\u003cli\u003e Equipped with a secure slide bolt latch for easy locking and unlocking\u003cli\u003e Includes a detachable handle for easy carrying with the ability to fold flat and lock for hassle-free transport and storage\u003cli\u003e Provides rubber feet to protect your floors\u003cli\u003e Crate mat sold separately\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003e Top Paw\u0026reg \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIncludes: \u003c/b\u003e 1 Folding Crate, 1 Divider Panel, 4 Roller Feet \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIntended Pet(s): \u003c/b\u003e Dogs \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eLife Stage:\u003c/b\u003e All Life Stages \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor: \u003c/b\u003e Black \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eMaterial(s): \u003c/b\u003e Wire\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eAssembly Instructions\u003c/b\u003e: Please refer to the \r\ninstruction manual for full operability and proper use.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n \r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCare Instructions\u003c/b\u003e: To protect the finish of the crate and the bottom of the pan, use only mild non-abrasive cleaners and water. Any coarse scrubbing or abrasive materials could damage finish. Use caution while cleaning. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWarning\u003c/b\u003e: For dogs only. To avoid injury or death, remove collar, tags, and leads before placing your pet in the crate.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaution: \u003c/b\u003eProduct may contain sharp edges. Not intended for children. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eAdvice for Use\u003c/b\u003e: Gradually help your dog become accustomed to being in the crate. Please read all instructions and guides before use.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eAbout the Top Paw\u0026reg Brand \u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nThe Top Paw\u0026reg brand guides pet parents through everyday pet care with a wide range of functional products and fashionable accessories. Our convenient and easy-to-use solutions, along with on-trend offerings, will help pet parents confidently care for their dogs throughout every stage of their lives. We aim to ensure that the functional and practical needs of dogs and those who love them are met. With such a diverse and extensive product assortment, we work hard to consider the intricacies of dog ownership and earn your trust.\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eAvailable Sizes and Dimensions:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cp\u003e\r\nSmall (dogs up to 22 inches long and up to 17 inches tall): 24.7 IN L X 17.5 IN W X 19.5 IN H (63 X 44.4 X 49.5 cm)\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nMedium (dogs up to 28 inches long and up to 19 inches tall): 30.67 IN L X 19.3 IN W X 21.46 IN H (77.9 X 49 X 54.5 cm)\u003cp\u003e\r\nMedium/Large (dogs up to 34 inches long and up to 22 inches tall): 36.6 IN L X 22.8 IN W X 24.8 IN H (93 X 58 X 63 cm)\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nLarge (dogs up to 40 inches long and up to 27 inches tall): 42.5 IN L X 28.5 IN W X 30.5 IN H (108 X 72.3 X 77.4 cm)\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nX-Large (dogs up to 45 inches long and up to 28.5 inches tall): 48.8 IN L X 30.1 IN W X 32 IN H (124 X 76.5 X 81.5 cm)","onlineFrom":1592524800000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"bed-sizeDisplays":null,"crateAndCarrier-sizeDisplays":["Large"],"crateAndCarrier-types":["Double Door"