,1597,1867,387,171,3250,2230,1023,3047,594,510,1558,1659,1221,1176,2218,1311,3097,729,1582,2422,422,2196,602,1412,2065,1227,2322,556,1039,1218,1182,1483,1220,450,3133,739,116,2775,140,3116,638,2395,1751,3010,2778,1964,2406,1084,1959,432,2502,1301,2469,471,81,1630,1353,1942,1393,787,2482,3063,1042,1196,1465,2354,673,221,1119,1333,600],"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":7.5,"cartonLength":4.75,"cartonWeight":1.541,"cartonWidth":4.75},"package":{"height":7.35,"length":4.7,"weight":2.03,"width":4.7},"brand":"Churu","customCategory":"Treats","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDESCRIPTION \u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e The lickable treats in this Inaba Churu Puree Tuna \u0026 Chicken Cat Treat Variety Pack are made with 100% pure and natural wild tuna or farm-raised chicken. Available in nine delectable varieties, Churu Purees are high in the moisture felines need for health. Simply tear open a tube and give it a little squeeze to feed these grain-free, preservative-free treats by hand. You can also pour them into a bowl or use as a tasty topper on wet or dry food.\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eKey Benefits: \u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eMade with 100% pure and natural wild tuna and farm-raised chicken\u003cli\u003eNo grains, preservatives or artificial colors\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture and savory flavors cats love\u003cli\u003eGreat for administering pills\u003cli\u003eHigh in moisture cats need for general health\u003cli\u003eLow in calories\u003cli\u003eDesigned for feeding by hand\u003cli\u003eInnovative, interactive way to spend time together\u003cli\u003eCan be used as a topper on wet or dry food\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5284731\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003e Inaba\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003e Tubes\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003e All\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNutritional Option: \u003c/b\u003e Grain-Free\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eFlavor:\u003c/b\u003e Tuna \u0026 Chicken\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eWeight:\u003c/b\u003e 50 Tubes\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNUTRITIONAL INFORMATION\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e    \r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eTUNA WITH CHICKEN RECIPE:\u003cbr\u003eWater, Tuna, Chicken, Tapioca, Natural Flavors, Guar Gum, Natural Tuna Flavor, Collagen, Vitamin E Supplement, Green Tea Extract\u003cp\u003eTUNA RECIPE:\u003cbr\u003eWater, Tuna, Tapioca, Natural Flavors, Guar Gum, Natural Tuna Flavor, Collagen, Vitamin E Supplement, Green Tea Extract\u003cp\u003eTUNA WITH SALMON RECIPE:\u003cbr\u003eWater, Tuna, Tapioca, Salmon, Natural Flavors, Natural Tuna Flavor, Guar Gum, Collagen, Vitamin E Supplement, Green Tea Extract\u003cp\u003eCHICKEN RECIPE:\u003cbr\u003eWater, Chicken, Tapioca, Natural Flavors, Natural Scallop Flavor, Guar Gum, Collagen, Vitamin E Supplement, Green Tea Extract\u003cp\u003eCHICKEN WITH CHEESE RECIPE:\u003cbr\u003eWater, Chicken, Cheese, Tapioca, Natural Flavors, Natural Chicken Flavor, Guar Gum, Collagen, Vitamin E Supplement, Green Tea Extract.\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Crude Protein (min) 7.00%\u003cbr\u003eCrude Fat (min) 0.20%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eCrude Fiber (max) 0.30%\u003cbr\u003eMoisture (max) 91.00%\u003cbr\u003eAsh (max) 1.50%\u003cbr\u003eCalcium (min) 0.003%\r\n\u003cbr\u003eMagnesium (max) 0.015%\u003cbr\u003ePhosphorus (min) 0.20%\u003cbr\u003ePotassium (min) 0.10%\u003cbr\u003eTaurine (min) 0.01%\u003cbr\u003eVitamin E (min) 310 IU/kg    \r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e (calculated): 430 kcal/kg, 6.0 kcal/tube ME\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFEEDING INSTRUCTIONS\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Feed as a treat to your cat.  This product is not intended to be fed as a meal.  Provide clean, fresh water daily.  Refrigerate after opening and server as soon as possible.","quantity":"50 Count","onlineFrom":1544918400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"catLifestages":["All Life Stages"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"packagingTypes":["Pouch","Tub","Variety Pack"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"quantityDisplays":["50-99 Count"],"treatTypes":["Lickable"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.9,"bvReviewCount":460,"conversionRate":75,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"INABA FOODS (USA) INC","manufacturerSku":"USA653A","isCaseRequiredSTH":false,"shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnlyOverride":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"857276007697","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":32.99,"strikethrough-number":42.99,"validUntil":"2028-01-01T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$32.99","strikethrough":"$42.99"},"displayType":"single"},"variations":["1 Size"],"categories":[[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"200146","name":{"default":"Treats"}},{"id":"200209","name":{"default":"Food and Treats"}},{"id":"200000","name":{"default":"Cat"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"SDDBOPIS","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery In Store Pick Up"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"60000060","name":{"default":"Curbside and In Store Pickup"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}]],"custom_category_names":["Cat","Cat \u003e Food and Treats","Cat \u003e Food and Treats \u003e Treats","Featured Shops","Featured Shops \u003e A