ultry with the 32 wet cat food pate cans in this Purina Friskies Pate Poultry Favorites wet canned cat food variety pack. With eight cans each of four delicious varieties \u0026ndash; including Poultry Platter, Chicken and Liver Dinner, Turkey and Giblets Dinner, and Mixed Grill \u0026ndash; each dinner option has a Friskies cat food taste cats love while adding healthy hydration to their diet. Real poultry is the number 1 ingredient in the Poultry Platter, helping deliver high\u0026ndash;quality protein to promote 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for the maintenance of adult cats. Added vitamins and minerals in each wet cat food pate variety also help give your cat what she needs to support her health. Plus, they all feature a turkey or chicken cat food wet pate taste that will have her running to the kitchen when she hears her dinner dish being set out. Feed your cat the excellent nutrition and great taste in this Friskies pate cat food variety pack and show her how much you love her.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eFour delicious Friskies cat food flavors to choose from at mealtime, including classic recipes made with real poultry for a taste cats love with no artificial colors or preservatives. Canned cat food pate variety pack containing essential vitamins and minerals and delivers 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for the maintenance of adult cats. Features a smooth wet cat food pate texture that is easy for any cat to handle. This Friskies canned cat food pate recipe is manufactured in Purina\u0026ndash;owned U.S. facilities and undergoes rigorous quality checks for added peace of mind. Friskies wet cat food pate variety pack checked for quality and safety and formulated to meet or exceed industry standards. Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5237486\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFriskies Pate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003ePate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eNo Artificial Colors, No Artificial Preservatives\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eMaintenance\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e12.93 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003ePat\u0026eacute; Turkey \u0026#38; Giblets Dinner: Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Water, Poultry By\u0026ndash;Products, Turkey, Poultry Giblets, Fish, Rice, Artificial And Natural Flavors, MINERALS [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Guar Gum, Salt, Tricalcium Phosphate, Carrageenan, Taurine, Choline Chloride, VITAMINS [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement,Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. H606123; Pat\u0026eacute; Mixed Grill: Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Water, Poultry By\u0026ndash;Products, Chicken, Fish, Rice, Artificial And Natural Flavors, Tricalcium Phosphate, MINERALS [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Guar Gum, Salt, Carrageenan, Choline Chloride, Taurine, VITAMINS [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vita