n used as directed. Slow\u0026ndash;release deodorizing system ensures continuous odor control, Forms strong, tight clumps for easy cleanup and scooping. Low dust cat litter formula for a clean pour, Tidy Cats litter with a clean linen scent. Clumping clay cat litter absorbs moisture to keep cats comfortable, Ideal for multiple\u0026ndash;cat households. Convenient packaging for easy storage, Simple form is easy to use. 24\u0026frasl;7 odor control helps you maintain a fresh\u0026ndash;smelling home, Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures: \u003c/b\u003eOdor Control\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003ePurina Tidy Cats Clumping Cat Litter, 24\u0026frasl;7 Performance Multi Cat Litter\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eMaterials: \u003c/b\u003ePlastic\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003ePackage Weight: \u003c/b\u003e2.1 lb\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eInstructions: \u003c/b\u003eStore in a dry place.\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1627257600000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"litter-features":["Advanced Odor Control","Clumping","Low Dust","Multi-Cat","Scented"],"litter-materials":["Clay"],"litter-types":["Clay"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.1,"bvReviewCount":6187,"conversionRate":80,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA ,","manufacturerSku":"7023001669","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"70230016690","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":19.69,"strikethrough-number":21.49,"validUntil":"2028-01-01T07:0