003e5 layers of leak protection\u003cli\u003eSwift Dry\u0026reg Technology quickly turns liquid to gel\u003cli\u003ePheromone attractant on top layer\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5277159\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003e Top Paw\u0026reg \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIncludes: \u003c/b\u003e50 Count \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eIntended Pet(s): \u003c/b\u003e Dogs \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eColor: \u003c/b\u003e White \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eHolds: \u003c/b\u003e 10 cups \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eDimensions:\u003c/b\u003e 28 IN L X 34 IN W (71.1 X 86.3 cm)\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eDirections:\u003c/b\u003e \u003cbr\u003e Step 1: Select an area away from your dog\u0026#39;s food and bed. Unfold the pad and place it on the floor, tissue side up. Secure with adhesive tabs.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eStep 2: Lead your dog to the pad to become accustomed to its scentand use. Repeat as needed until your dog is comfortable using the pad.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eStep 3: Reward your dog for correctly using the pad. Dispose of the pad in a trash receptacle. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaution: \u003c/b\u003e FOR DOG USE ONLY. Do not let your dog chew or eat the pads. THIS IS NOT A TOY. Keep out of reach of children.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eAdvice for Use:\u003c/b\u003e Make sure to train your dog with the pads before leaving them alone for best training results. \u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eAbout the Top Paw\u0026reg Brand\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nThe Top Paw\u0026reg brand guides pet parents through everyday pet care with a wide range of functional products and fashionable accessories. Our convenient and easy-to-use solutions and on-trend offerings will help pet parents confidently care for their dogs through every stage of their lives. We aim to ensure that the functional and practical needs of dogs and those who love them are met. With such a diverse and extensive product assortment, we work hard to consider the intricacies of dog ownership and gain your trust. \u003cbr\u003e","quantity":"50 Count","onlineFrom":1517875200000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"quantityDisplays":["50-99 Count"],"avalaraTaxCode":"111","bvAverageRating":4.7,"bvReviewCount":1318,"conversionRate":115,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"TIANJIN YIYI HYGIENE PRODUCTS","manufacturerSku":"TP XXL 50CT-2","shipToHome-isCASupported":true,"shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"196481056374","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":39.99,"strikethrough-number":null,"validUntil":"","formatted":{"primary":"$39.99"},"displayType":"single"},"variations":["1 Size"],"categories":[[{"id":"S03-Dog","name":{"default":"Dog Sale"}},{"id":"S03","name":{"default":"March"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"100262","name":{"default":"Potty Training"}},{"id":"100412","name":{"default":"Training and Behavior"}},{"id":"100000","name":{"default":"Dog"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"AFD-01","name":{"default":"Anything for Dogs"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"5000260","name":{"default":"Top Paw"}},{"id":"5000000","name":{"default":"Featured Brands"}}],[{"id":"SDDBOPIS","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery In Store Pick Up"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"60000060","na