\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNUTRITIONAL INFORMATION\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e    \r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Deboned Chicken, Chicken Meal, Brown Rice, Oat Groats, Barley, Chicken Fat (Preserved With Mixed Tocopherols), Natural Flavor, Whole Flaxseed, Pea Fiber, Potassium Chloride, Dried Chicory Root, Dried Carrots, Dried Kale, Dried Pumpkin, Dried Blueberries, Minerals (Zinc Sulfate, Zinc Proteinate, Iron Proteinate, Ferrous Sulfate, Copper Proteinate, Manganese Sulfate, Sodium Selenite, Manganese Proteinate, Copper Sulfate), Vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, Vitamin A Supplement, Niacin Supplement, d-Calcium Pantothenate, Riboflavin Supplement, Thiamine Mononitrate, Biotin, Vitamin B12 Supplement, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Calcium Iodate, Folic Acid, Vitamin D3 Supplement), Choline Chloride, DL-Methionine, Citric Acid (A Preservative), Mixed Tocopherols (A Preservative), Rosemary Extract\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e   Crude Protein (min) 25.0% \u003cbr\u003eCrude Fat (min) 13.0% \u003cbr\u003eCrude Fiber (max) 5.5%\u003cbr\u003e Moisture (max) 10.0% \u003cbr\u003eCalcium (min) 1.2%\u003cbr\u003ePhosphorus (min) 0.8%\u003cbr\u003ePotassium (min) 0.6%\u003cbr\u003eZinc (min) 175 mg/kg\u003cbr\u003eSelenium (min) 0.35 mg/kg\u003cbr\u003eVitamin A (min) 20,000 IU/kg\u003cbr\u003eVitamin E (min) 200 IU/kg\u003cbr\u003eOmega-6 Fatty Acids** (min) 2.0%\u003cbr\u003eOmega-3 Fatty Acids** (min) 0.3%\u003cbr\u003e**Not recognized as an essential nutrient by the AAFCO Dog Food Nutrient Profiles.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e 3,668 kcal/kg, 380 kcal/cup\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFEEDING INSTRUCTIONS\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e For adult dogs, feed Simply Nourish Chicken \u0026 Brown Rice Recipe Adult Dog Food either dry or moistened with water. Begin with the recommendations provided and adjust to maintain body weight. Dogs may be fed once or twice per day. Water: Provide your dog with fresh water in a clean container daily. Always consult your veterinarian with any health questions. Wash hands with soap and warm water after handling.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlease follow specific daily feeding instructions included on packaging.","onlineFrom":1648425600000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"dogLifestages":["All Life Stages"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"kibbleSizes":["All Breeds"],"customPet":["Dog"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.3,"bvReviewCount":903,"conversionRate":85,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"DIAMOND PET FOODS","manufacturerSku":"10037","shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStorePickUp":true,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"737257969216","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":52.99,"strikethrough-number":59.99,"validUntil":"9999-12-31T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$14.99-$52.99","strikethrough":"$14.99-$59.99"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["4 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"100246","name":{"default":"Dry Food"}},{"id":"100409","name":{"default":"Food"}},{"id":"100000","name":{"default":"Dog"}}],[{"id":"S03-Dog","name":{"default":"Dog Sale"}},{"id":"S03","name":{"default":"March"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"S03Dog-10X","name":{"default":"10x Dog Large Food Bags"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"AFD-01","name":{"default