,568,386,3021,2752,2226,2513,2248,1178,1240,2196,1153,1209,1215,573,2186,2046,675,336,2720,55,2265,2198,672,128,2311,3061,1219,2436,1279,232,2395,2212,1476,1174,1703,1941,1570,624,1648,1186,516,441,2327,1554,1465,1963,1239,642],"size":{"solidSize":"30 Lb"},"flavor":{"value":"Chicken, Turkey, Salmon \u0026 Oceanfish","displays":"Chicken, Fish, Salmon, Turkey"},"dimensionsAndWeight":{"cartonHeight":24,"cartonLength":5,"cartonWeight":30.427,"cartonWidth":19},"package":{"height":5,"length":24,"weight":30,"width":19},"brand":"Meow Mix","customCategory":"Dry Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eDelight your cat with the Original Choice for everyday nutrition \u0026ndash; and taste that hits. Meow Mix Original Choice Dry Cat Food is made with the irresistible flavors of chicken, turkey, salmon and ocean fish to get 'em purring for mealtime. And you can feel the excitement too, knowing that this formula provides the one\u0026ndash;hundred percent complete and balanced nutrition your cat needs every day. That includes 40 essential vitamins, minerals, amino acids and fatty acids, along with high quality protein that helps support a lean energetic body. And don't forget the antioxidants, which help support a long, healthy life. With so much goodness packed into every bite, it's no wonder why Meow Mix cat food is The Only One Cats Ask for by Name.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eContains one (1) 30\u0026ndash;pound bag of Meow Mix Original Choice Dry Cat Food More of the flavor cats love One hundred percent complete and balanced nutrition for adult cats High quality protein helps support strong, healthy muscles Produced in the U.S.A. from globally sourced ingredients\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCat\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eMeow Mix\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eKibble\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAdult\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eChicken, Turkey, Salmon \u0026#38; Ocean Fish\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e30 lb\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eGround Corn, Chicken By\u0026ndash;Product Meal, Soybean Meal, Corn Protein Meal, Beef Tallow (Mixed Tocopherols Used As A Preservative), Natural Flavor, Turkey By\u0026ndash;Product Meal, Salmon Meal, Ocean Fish Meal (Ethoxyquin Used As A Preservative), Calcium Carbonate, Phosphoric Acid, Sodium Acid Pyrophosphate, Choline Chloride, Salt, Vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin Supplement, Vitamin A Supplement, Thiamine Mononitrate, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, D\u0026ndash;Calcium Pantothenate, Riboflavin Supplement, Vitamin B12 Supplement, Folic Acid, Biotin, Vitamin D3 Supplement), Dl\u0026ndash;Methionine, Taurine, Minerals (Ferrous Sulfate, Zinc Oxide, Manganous Oxide, Copper Sulfate, Sodium Selenite, Calcium Iodate), Yellow 6, Red 40, Yellow 5, Lactic Acid, Potassium Chloride, L\u0026ndash;Lysine Monohydrochloride, Blue 2, Rosemary Extract\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003e308 kcal ME/cup\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eCrude Protein (Min): 30%Crude Fat (Min): 11%Crude Fiber (Max): 4%Moisture (Max): 12%Calcium (Min): 1%Phosphorus (Min): 0.8%Selenuim (Min): 0.3 mg\u0026frasl;kgVitamin E (Min): 50 IU\u0026frasl;kg\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeeding Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eA single morning serving will allow your cat to nibble freely throughout the day. The serving size should be adjusted based on your cat's age and activity level. When introducing Meow Mix Original Choice cat food, gradually mix it with your cat's current food over the course of 7\u0026ndash;10 days. Always provide your cat with a bowl of fresh water. Weight of Adult Cat (Over 1 Year) ... Cups per Day* 5\u0026ndash;10 lb ... 1/2\u0026ndash;3/4 cup 11\u0026ndash;16 lb ... 3/4\u0026ndash;1 cup *Using a standard 8\u0026ndash;oz measuringcup. Kittens (Under 1 Year) Feed 2 times the adult requirement. Pregnant and Nursing Cats Feed 2\u0026ndash;4 times the adult requirement.\u003c/p\u003e","foodCategory":"Value Brands","onlineFrom":1664582400000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"catLifestages":["All Life Stages"],"environments":["Indoor","Outdoor"],"foodForms":["Dry"],"foodPoundsSizeDisplays":["24 Lb and Over"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"packagingTypes":["Bag"],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.5,"bvReviewCount":4984,"conversionRate":60,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"SMUCKER RETAIL FOODS INC","manufacturerSku":"00829274520997","shoppingOptions-isBopisEligible":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreAvailable":true,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"customScheduledDeliveryEligible":true,"isSubscriptionEnabled":true,"isInStockInStore":true,"upc":"829274520997","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":29.99,"strikethrough-number":null,"validUntil":"","formatted":{"primary":"$5.69-$29.99","strikethrough":"$7.99-$29.99"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["5 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"60080122","name":{"default":"Timezone Test"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"S03Cat-10X","name":{"default":"10x Cat Large Food Bags "}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"ME01","name":{"default":"March Event"}},{"id":"sale","name":{"default":"Sale"}}],[{"id":"500425","name":{"default":"Meow Mix"}},{"id":"5000000","na