:{"height":7.6,"length":7.9,"weight":6.66,"width":5.4},"brand":"Fancy Feast","customCategory":"Canned Food","long_description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eDescription: \u003c/b\u003eLet Fancy Feast delight your cat with an exceptional mealtime experience every time you open a can from this Fancy Feast Grilled Cat Food Seafood Collection in Gravy Cat Food. Crafted in partnership with our expert chefs and nutritionists, these protein\u0026ndash;rich, canned cat food variety pack features the irresistible of real seafood while delivering 100 percent complete and balanced nourishment. Also included in this flavorful, high\u0026ndash;quality soft cat food collection are vitamins and minerals to support your cat's whole\u0026ndash;body health and a light, savory cat food gravy to tempt their tastebuds. This premium canned cat food collection is made without artificial colors or preservatives, so you know your cat is getting everything they need and nothing they don't. Show your cat how much you care with a Grilled Fancy Feast wet cat food variety pack and watch them savor the spellbinding aroma, enticing texture and delectable flavor sensation down to the very last bite.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeatures \u0026 Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eFancy Feast wet cat food made without artificial colors or preservatives. Crafted with real, high\u0026ndash;quality ingredients to deliver 100 percent complete and balanced canned cat food. Fancy Feast grilled cat food developed in partnership with our expert nutritionists to create a unique and unforgettable taste experience for your cat. Crafted with real seafood in a light, savory gravy for cats. Protein\u0026ndash;rich, gourmet soft cat food recipe creates a flavor\u0026ndash;filled experience, with savory gravy adds to the delicious taste. Spoil your pet with Purina products. Reward yourself with points on every purchase. Download the myPurina app today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eItem Number: \u003c/b\u003e 5263573\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBrand: \u003c/b\u003eFancy Feast Grilled\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFood Type: \u003c/b\u003eGrilled\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreed Size: \u003c/b\u003eAll Breeds\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLife Stage: \u003c/b\u003eAll Stages\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eNutritional Benefits: \u003c/b\u003eWith Vitamins, No Artificial Colors, No Artificial Preservatives\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHealth Consideration: \u003c/b\u003eMaintenance\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFlavor: \u003c/b\u003eSeafood, Tuna, Salmon\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWeight: \u003c/b\u003e6.66 lb.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients: \u003c/b\u003eGrilled Salmon Feast in Gravy: Fish Broth, Salmon, Wheat Gluten, Chicken, Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Liver, Corn Starch\u0026ndash;Modified, Soy Flour, Glycine, Salt, Tricalcium Phosphate, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Natural Flavor, Taurine, Choline Chloride, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. E692622Grilled Seafood Feast in Gravy: Fish Broth, Ocean Fish, Wheat Gluten, Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Liver, Chicken, Corn Starch\u0026ndash;Modified, Soy Flour, Corn Oil, Shrimp, Glycine, Salt, Tricalcium Phosphate, Natural Flavor, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Choline Chloride, Taurine, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. E692822Grilled Tuna Feast in Gravy: Fish Broth, Tuna, Wheat Gluten, Chicken, Meat By\u0026ndash;Products, Liver, Corn Starch\u0026ndash;Modified, Soy Flour, Corn Oil, Glycine, Salt, Tricalcium Phosphate, Natural Flavor, Minerals [Potassium Chloride, Magnesium Proteinate, Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Potassium Iodide], Taurine, Choline Chloride, Vitamins [Thiamine Mononitrate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;1), Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;3), Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;5), Vitamin A Supplement, Menadione Sodium Bisulfite Complex (Vitamin K), Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;6), Riboflavin Supplement (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;2), Vitamin B\u0026ndash;12 Supplement, Biotin (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;7), Folic Acid (Vitamin B\u0026ndash;9), Vitamin D\u0026ndash;3 Supplement]. E692922\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eGuaranteed Analysis: \u003c/b\u003eGrilled Salmon Feast in Gravy: Crude Protein (Min)\u0026hellip;11.0%, Crude Fat (Min)\u0026hellip;1.5%, Crude Fiber (Max)\u0026hellip;1.5%. Moisture (Max)\u0026hellip;80.0%, Ash (Max)\u0026hellip;2.7%, Taurine (Min)\u0026hellip;0.05%. Grilled Seafood Feast in Gravy: Crude Protein (Min)\u0026hellip;11.0%, Crude Fat (Min)\u0026hellip;2.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)\u0026hellip;1.5%, Moisture (Max)\u0026hellip;80.0%, Ash (Max)\u0026hellip;2.7%, Taurine (Min)\u0026hellip;0.05%. Grilled Tuna Feast in Gravy: Crude Protein (Min)\u0026hellip;11.0%, Crude Fat (Min)\u0026hellip;2.0%, Crude Fiber (Max)\u0026hellip;1.5%, Moisture (Max)\u0026hellip;80.0%, Ash (Max)\u0026hellip;2.7%, Taurine (Min)\u0026hellip;0.05%.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eCaloric Content: \u003c/b\u003eGrilled Salmon Feast in Gravy: 850 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 72 kcal\u0026frasl;can, Grilled Seafood Feast in Gravy: 843 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 71 kcal\u0026frasl;can, Grilled Tuna Feast in Gravy: 841 kcal\u0026frasl;kg, 71 kcal\u0026frasl;can\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eFeeding Instructions: \u003c/b\u003eFeed an average size adult cat 1 can per 3 pounds of body weight daily. Feed up to twice this amount to kittens. Pregnant or nursing cats may require two to four times their normal feeding.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSpecies: \u003c/b\u003eCat\u003c/p\u003e","onlineFrom":1486080000000,"onlineTo":4102444799000,"catLifestages":["All Life Stages"],"environments":["Any"],"foodOuncesSizeDisplays":["16 Oz and Over"],"foodTextures":["Grilled"],"customHealthConsideration":["General Health"],"packagingTypes":["Variety Pack"],"petType-breeds":[""],"customPet":["Cat"],"productAvailabilityLocations":["In Store"],"series":["FANCY FEAST MAINLINE","Purina Cat Food \u0026 Treats"],"avalaraTaxCode":"EEE","bvAverageRating":4.8,"bvReviewCount":3546,"conversionRate":95,"customBvAverageRating":4,"manufacturerName":"NESTLE PURINA WET","manufacturerSku":"00-50000-58664","shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnly":false,"shoppingOptions-isInStoreOnlyOverride":false,"shoppingOptions-isSoldOnlineOnly":false,"isInStockInStore":false,"upc":"50000586646","isSearchableFlag":true,"isSKUAvailable":true,"price":{"number":28.06,"strikethrough-number":28.97,"validUntil":"9999-12-31T07:00:00.000Z","formatted":{"primary":"$22.86-$28.06","strikethrough":"$23.37-$28.97"},"displayType":"range"},"variations":["2 Sizes","1 Flavor"],"categories":[[{"id":"6000030","name":{"default":"Auto ship"}},{"id":"6000000","name":{"default":"Featured Shops"}}],[{"id":"6007000","name":{"default":"Same Day Delivery"}},{"id":"6